NK030(a)005:2: dngos grub blangs pa'i cho ga bzhugs soha&a&a&a //
NK030(a)005:3: gnyis pa dngos grub len pa la gnyis te /
NK030(a)005:4: 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub len pa dang /
NK030(a)005:5: dam rdzas la rten nas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub len pa'o //
NK030(a)005:7: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK030(a)005:11: tshad dang ldan pa'i sa stegs la /
NK030(a)005:13: thig skud rab gnas dang ldan pas /
NK030(a)005:16: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK030(a)005:17: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK030(a)005:18: gsum pa bzhi pa phyi ma gdab //
NK030(a)005:19: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab /
NK030(a)005:20: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK030(a)005:21: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK030(a)005:22: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK030(a)005:23: cha chen gcig nas lte ba skor //
NK030(a)005:24: cha chen gnyis nas rtsibs bzhi bskor //
NK030(a)005:25: cha chen gsum nas rtsib bzhi bskor //
NK030(a)005:26: cha chen bzhi nas rtsibs bcu bskor //
NK030(a)005:27: cha chen bdun du glang gur dang rdo ra bskor /
NK030(a)005:28: cha chen brgyad kyi phyir rol pad+ma dang /
NK030(a)005:33: de'i rgyab tu yang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK030(a)005:34: de rgyab tu 'khor lo rtsibs bcu gru chad sgo la sogs dal spyi dang mthun par bri'o //
NK030(a)005:35: de nas tshon rtsi rab gnas dang ldan bas /
NK030(a)005:44: sgo la sogs dkyil 'khor spyi dang mthun par mdzes shing /
NK030(a)005:46: de nas lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i tshom bu dang /
NK030(a)005:47: tsa ka li rnams lha rang gnas su dgod /
NK030(a)005:49: las bum rnams gang bder bgod /
NK030(a)005:53: tshe chang rnams gang bder bshams /
NK030(a)005:54: byang shar du mtshams 'dzin gyi me tog /
NK030(a)005:61: byang du zhal zas rnams bshams /
NK030(a)005:62: de nas shar lhor bla ma'i gtor ma /
NK030(a)005:63: shar du yi dam tshe dpag med kyi gtor ma /
NK030(a)005:67: byang shar du mkha' 'gro ma'i gtor ma /
NK030(a)005:68: byang du chos skyong ma mo nub byang du mgon po /
NK030(a)005:72: gtor ma rnams la chab dang /
NK030(a)005:74: de nas dpon slob rnams gdan la bzhugs la rab gnas kyi dod du /
NK030(a)005:77: mdun bskyed gsum gyi dang po ni /
NK030(a)005:78: mdun gyi nam mkhar dkon mchog drug po sgom la /
NK030(a)005:79: bdag dang 'gro ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems thams cad /
NK030(a)005:80: dus 'di nas bzung ste byang chub ma thob kyi bar du /
NK030(a)005:81: bla ma la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK030(a)005:82: sangs rgyas la skyabs su chos la skyabs dge 'dun
NK030(a)005:83: la yi dam gyi lha tshogs rnams la skyabs su
NK030(a)005:84: mkha' 'gro dang chos skyong rnams la skyabs su mchi'o
NK030(a)005:88: sems can thams cad kyi don du bdag sangs rgyas thob par bya /
NK030(a)005:89: de'i ched du mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa'i bsgom bzlas kyi rim pa la 'jug /
NK030(a)005:90: sems can thams cad bde ba dang bde ba'i rgyu dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:91: sdug bsngal dang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:92: sdug bsngal med pa'i bde ba dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:93: nye ring chags sdang gnyis dang bral ba'i btang snyoms la gnas par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:94: nye ring chags sdang gnyis dang bral ba'i btang snyoms la gnas par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:95: de nas rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)005:96: swa b+ha wa shud d+ha sarba d+harma swa b+ha wa shu d+ho ham /
NK030(a)005:97: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+aum las /
NK030(a)005:98: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK030(a)005:100: nang pad+ma ra ga las grub pa gru bzhi /
NK030(a)005:107: dril bu dang dril bu chen po'i sgra 'khrol ba /
NK030(a)005:115: zhing khams rnam par dag pa'i dbus su /
NK030(a)005:116: gser las grub pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi nyis rim /
NK030(a)005:117: de'i rgyab tsakra rtsibs bcu dkar po /
NK030(a)005:118: dbus kyi lte bar rin chen khri rma bya brgyad kyi nye bar bteg pa /
NK030(a)005:119: dar ljang khu'i khri khebs de'i steng du pad+ma nyi ma zla ba'i gdan /
NK030(a)005:120: rtsibs phyi nang brgyad la zla ba'i gdan /
NK030(a)005:121: rtsib bcu la nyi ma bcu /
NK030(a)005:122: sgo bzhi la zla ba'i gdan no /
NK030(a)005:123: de nas brten pa lha bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)005:124: dbus kyi gdan gyi steng du /
NK030(a)005:125: rang gi sems kyi ngo bo h+aum dmar ser /
NK030(a)005:129: byin rlabs dngos grub nus mthu thams cad tshur 'dus h+aum la thim /
NK030(a)005:133: bdag nyid tshe dpag tu med pa //
NK030(a)005:134: sku mdog dmar ser zhal gcig phyag gnyis //
NK030(a)005:136: phyag g.yas skyabs sbyin gyi phyag rgya thugs kar mdzad pa /
NK030(a)005:137: g.yon pa mnyam bzhag gi steng du /
NK030(a)005:138: gser las grub pa'i bum pa /
NK030(a)005:139: 'chi med bdud rtsi bkang nas 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)005:140: dar dmar po'i mgul chings dang /
NK030(a)005:141: dpag bsam shing ljang khu'i kha brgyan can //
NK030(a)005:142: zhabs rdo rje skyil dkrungs gis bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)005:143: dar ser po'i stod g.yogs kha dog lnga'i smad dkris /
NK030(a)005:144: rin po che'i dbu brgyan dang /
NK030(a)005:152: sku la mtshan bzang po sum bcu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK030(a)005:153: dpe byad bzang po brgyad bcu dang ldan pa /
NK030(a)005:155: / 'od zer stong phrag du ma dang ldan pa //
NK030(a)005:157: yum sangs rgyas spyan ma sku mdog dkar mo //
NK030(a)005:158: phyag g.yas pa tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)005:159: g.yon pas tshe'i bum pa bsnam pa /
NK030(a)005:160: de ni sku mchog nyid kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)005:161: de nas yab kyi thugs kar rdo rje rgya gram gyi gur khang /
NK030(a)005:162: de'i nang du nyi zla ga'u kha sbyor gyi gur khang /
NK030(a)005:163: de gnyis ni thabs shes kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)005:164: de'i nang du 'khor lo dkar po gyis 'a khrigs pa'i gur /
NK030(a)005:165: de'i nang du pad+ma dmar po as 'khrigs pa'i gur /
NK030(a)005:166: de'i nang du rdo rje sngon po h+aum gis 'a khrigs pa'i gur khang /
NK030(a)005:167: de ni sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)005:168: de'i nang du 'od zer dkar po gyis 'khrigs pa /
NK030(a)005:171: dmar po am 'od zer ljang khus has 'khrigs pa'i gur khang /
NK030(a)005:172: de ni ye shes lnga'i phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)005:173: de'i nang du gser las grub pa'i tsakra rtsibs brgyad
NK030(a)005:174: pa mgo ma'i ri'u mig brgyad la gser gyi zor
NK030(a)005:176: yu ba la yi ge tram gyis mtshan pa /
NK030(a)005:178: de ni gser gyi zor pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)005:179: de'i nang pad nyi'i gdan la /
NK030(a)005:180: hrihdamara po zung gcig 'od du zhu //
NK030(a)005:182: dpal rta mgrin sku mdog dmar ser //
NK030(a)005:185: phyag g.yas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)005:186: g.yon pas tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa //
NK030(a)005:187: zhabs gnyis rkyang brkum gyis 'gying bzhin bzhugs pa rta
NK030(a)005:188: mgo ljang khu rngog ma leb rgan nam mkha'i dbyings
NK030(a)005:189: su 'tsher ba // de'i pang du yum rdo rje phag mo sku mdog dmar mo //
NK030(a)005:190: phyag g.yas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa //
NK030(a)005:191: g.yon pa tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa yab yum gnyis ka dpal chas dang /
NK030(a)005:192: dur khrod kyichasa kyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)005:193: 'tshams rngam gzi byin dang bcas nas bskal pa'i me dpung gi nang du bzhugs pa /
NK030(a)005:194: de ni rta mchog dbang gi phyag rgya'o //
NK030(a)005:195: yab rta mgrin gyi thugs kar /
NK030(a)005:196: bdag gi bkrag mdangs kyi ngo bo 'od phung dkar
NK030(a)005:197: po tshon gang tsam gcig mar me rlung gi ma
NK030(a)005:198: skyod pa lta bu gcig bsam /
NK030(a)005:199: de'i nang du rnam shes kyi ngo bo h+aum dmar ser 'bur du langs pa gcig bsam /
NK030(a)005:201: tshe'i ngo bo a dkar po gcig bsam /
NK030(a)005:202: de'i dpung ba g.yas kyi nang du /
NK030(a)005:203: srog gi sa bon n+ri dkar ljang re krangs kyis bsam /
NK030(a)005:204: dpung pa g.yon du ming yig dang po krangs kyi bsam /
NK030(a)005:205: bar du bla'i ngo bo spu dmar ser krangs kyis bsam /
NK030(a)005:206: de rnams kyi steng du dkar po /
NK030(a)005:211: de rnams kyi rgyab du a yu b+hi ru dz+nya na badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)005:212: tshe b+h+rum ni dzah pun+ye pun+ye ma h+aa pun+ye //
NK030(a)005:213: a pa ra mi ta a yuhpun+ye dz+nya na ro pa tsit+ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)005:216: b+h+rum ka ba tsa rak+sha rak+sha h+aum //
NK030(a)005:218: de ni chos kyi dbyings kyi phyag rgya'o /
NK030(a)005:219: gtso bo tshe dpag med yab yum gyi phyi rol
NK030(a)005:220: du pad nyi'i gdan la rta mgrin gong du bsgom
NK030(a)005:221: pa lta bu gshog rtse bsnol ba'i gur khang gcig
NK030(a)005:222: sgom pa ni gtso bo yum bskyed pa'o //
NK030(a)005:223: de'i rgyab rtsibs nang ma bzhi la //
NK030(a)005:224: h+aum dkar ser dmar ljang bzhi las 'od zer 'phros /
NK030(a)005:228: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK030(a)005:229: shar du tshe'i lha mo dkar mo //
NK030(a)005:230: phyag g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)005:231: g.yon shel gyi tshe bum bsnams pa /
NK030(a)005:232: lhor tshe'i lha mor ser mo /
NK030(a)005:234: g.yon pas bee d+aur+ya'i tshe yi bum pa bsnams pa //
NK030(a)005:235: nub du tshe'i lha mor dmar mo //
NK030(a)005:236: g.yas pa tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu /
NK030(a)005:237: g.yon pas byi ru'i tshe yi bum pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)005:238: byang du tshe'i lha mo ljang khu //
NK030(a)005:239: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)005:240: g.yon pas in+t+ra ni la'i tshe bum bsnam pa'o //
NK030(a)005:245: ho ljang khu bzhi la 'od 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur ba las /
NK030(a)005:246: shar du dbyings kyi lha mo dkar mo //
NK030(a)005:247: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)005:248: lhor dbyings kyi lha mo ser mo //
NK030(a)005:249: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i zhags pa //
NK030(a)005:250: nub du dbyings kyi lha mo dmar mo //
NK030(a)005:251: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags sgrogs //
NK030(a)005:252: byang du dbyings kyi lha mo ljang khu //
NK030(a)005:253: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i dril bu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)005:254: g.yon pa bzhi na tshe'i bum ba bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)005:256: h+aum dkar po bcu las 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK030(a)005:258: phyag g.yas pa bcu na tshe 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)005:261: spyan gsum stag sham sprul brgyan dang //
NK030(a)005:262: rin po che rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK030(a)005:267: ho ljang khu bzhi las 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK030(a)005:268: shar sgor stag gdong ma dkar mo //
NK030(a)005:269: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin ba'i lcags kyu //
NK030(a)005:270: lho sgor phag gdong ma ser mo //
NK030(a)005:271: g.yas pas tshe 'dzin pa'i zhags pa //
NK030(a)005:272: nub sgor kha gdong ma dmar mo nyi zla'i spyan can //
NK030(a)005:274: byang sgor 'ug gdong ma ljang khu //
NK030(a)005:276: g.yon ba bzhi na bum pa bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)005:277: lha mo bcu gnyis po de dag rnams ni //
NK030(a)005:279: zhabs gnyis rkyang skum gar thabs //
NK030(a)005:283: gzhal yas khang de'i rgyab phyi bum pa'i nang du //
NK030(a)005:288: g.yon pa bcus lcags kyu bsnams pa //
NK030(a)005:289: spyan gsum 'jigs pa'i 'tshams rngam me ri dang bcas pa //
NK030(a)005:290: zhal phyir gyur nas tshe'i bar chad kyi bgegs bskrad pas bsgom mo //
NK030(a)005:291: de rnams ni 'khor lo bskyed pa'o //
NK030(a)005:292: de nas dngos grub kyi bcud bsdu ba ni //
NK030(a)005:293: rang gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros //
NK030(a)005:294: rta mgrin gyi mgrin pa nas //
NK030(a)005:295: shangs khung nas tshe dpag med kyi mgrin pa nas shangs khung nas 'phros /
NK030(a)005:296: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten la phog /
NK030(a)005:297: sa zhom pa yang spang sngo kad kyi gyur /
NK030(a)005:298: r+ts+wa skam yang me tog bkra kad kyi gyur /
NK030(a)005:299: shing skam po yang lo 'dab sngo dpar gyis gyur /
NK030(a)005:300: chu skam po yang dkar nar gyis gyur //
NK030(a)005:302: rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad 'od zer tsha ler gyur par bsam /
NK030(a)005:304: / 'od zer snga ma des sbrang mas sbrang rtsi bsdud pa ltar //
NK030(a)005:305: shing dang sa chu me rlung gi snod 'byung ba
NK030(a)005:306: chen po'i bcud bkrag mdangs rnams 'ub kyi bsdus nas
NK030(a)005:307: / rang tshe dpag med kyi shangs khung nas rim
NK030(a)005:308: bzhi sngar yar rgyud pa ltar brgyud nas thugs ka'i
NK030(a)005:309: h+aum a n+ri la sogs thim pas tshe bsod nams
NK030(a)005:310: thams cad bkrag gzi mdangs la sogs pa rgyas shing
NK030(a)005:311: / / tshe'i dngos grub thob bar bsam la //
NK030(a)005:312: a yu b+hi ru dza na badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)005:313: tshe b+h+rum n+rii dza bgrang ngo //
NK030(a)005:314: yang thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer snga ma bzhin spros //
NK030(a)005:315: nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad la phog pas //
NK030(a)005:316: sems can thams cad tshe nyams pa thams cad sor chud /
NK030(a)005:319: mi dang mi ma yin pa /
NK030(a)005:320: lha klu sde brgyad la sogs pa /
NK030(a)005:321: tshe bkrag mdangs dang ldan par bsam //
NK030(a)005:322: de nas 'od zer snga ma des //
NK030(a)005:324: lha klu sde brgyad khyad par du yang byad ma
NK030(a)005:325: lha dang bcas pa'i tshe dang bsod nams dpal dang
NK030(a)005:326: 'byor pa bkrag mdangs thams cad bkug nas /
NK030(a)005:327: rang gi shangs khungs nas yar brgyud pa bzhin bkug nas /
NK030(a)005:328: thugs kha'i 'od phung dang h+aum a n+ri yig 'bru rnams la thim pas //
NK030(a)005:329: tshe dang bsod nams dpal dang 'byor pa nyams pa sor chud pa dang //
NK030(a)005:330: rtogs pa sku dang ye shes thams cad rgyas par bsam la /
NK030(a)005:331: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK030(a)005:333: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs nas chos spyod byed pa ni //
NK030(a)005:334: lha tshogs thams cad kyi spyi bor /
NK030(a)005:337: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad la phog /
NK030(a)005:339: chos kyi sku rnams gzungs kyi skur bzhengs //
NK030(a)005:340: de rnams yang tshe dpag med 'khor dang bcas par gyur nas mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs /
NK030(a)005:341: hrih nub phyogs bde ba chen po'i pho brang nas //
NK030(a)005:342: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:343: tshe'i lha mo rnams kyis 'khor gyi bskor //
NK030(a)005:344: ye shes khro bo chen po bcu //
NK030(a)005:345: sgo ma bzhi po 'khor dang bcas //
NK030(a)005:347: badz+ra sa ma ya dza dzah dzahh+aum bam hohganyisa su med par bstim /
NK030(a)005:348: slar yang dbang gi lha tshogs rnams spyan drangs bas dbang bskur bar bsam la //
NK030(a)005:349: h+aum bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:350: thugs rje'i sku mchog yon tan rgya mtsho'i gter //
NK030(a)005:351: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi gzhal yas nas //
NK030(a)005:352: tshe'i lha mo ye shes g.yung drung dpal gyi sku //
NK030(a)005:353: gnyis med byang chub bde mchog rol pa thabs kyi gtso //
NK030(a)005:354: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:355: byang chub sems rgyun ye shes bdud rtsi 'dis //
NK030(a)005:356: skal ldan rnams la tshe'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:358: zhes byang chub sems kyi bdud rtsis dbang bskur //
NK030(a)005:359: dri ma dag chu lhag ma yar lud pas rigs lngas dbu brgyan /
NK030(a)005:360: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lngas byin gyis rlabs //
NK030(a)005:361: de nas rang gis thugs ka nas h+aum dkar dmar ljang gi tshogs spros //
NK030(a)005:362: mchod yon ma sogs la phog 'od du zhu ba las /
NK030(a)005:363: mchod yon ma dkar mo phyag na mchod yon //
NK030(a)005:364: bsnams pa'i tshogs dpag tu med pa spros nas //
NK030(a)005:365: lha tshogs rnams la mchod par phul bar bsam //
NK030(a)005:366: me tog la sogs kyang des 'gre /
NK030(a)005:367: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yis //
NK030(a)005:368: lha rdzas bzang po'i mchod yon rnams //
NK030(a)005:369: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:370: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)005:371: bzhes na tshe'i dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)005:374: gtsang zhing gtsang mar spyar ba yis //
NK030(a)005:375: lha rdzas bzang po'i me tog rnams //
NK030(a)005:376: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:377: tshe sring srog skyobs lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)005:378: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)005:379: badz+ra push+pe gtsang zhing gtsang mar spyar ba yis //
NK030(a)005:380: lha rdzas bzang po'i bdug spos 'di //
NK030(a)005:381: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:382: tshe sring srog skyobs lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)005:383: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)005:384: badz+ra d+hupe gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yis //
NK030(a)005:385: lha rdzas bzang po'i snang gsal 'di //
NK030(a)005:386: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:387: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)005:388: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:389: badz+ra a lo ke gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yis //
NK030(a)005:390: lhas rdzas bzang po'i dri chab rnams //
NK030(a)005:391: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:392: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //
NK030(a)005:393: bzhes nas tshe'i dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:394: badz+ra g+han+he gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi /
NK030(a)005:395: lha rdzas bzang po'i zhal zas rnams //
NK030(a)005:396: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:397: tshe sring srog skyob lha la 'bul //

NK030(a)005:756: slob ma bzhug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK030(a)005:758: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK030(a)005:760: slob ma dkyil 'khor bzhugs cing dbang bskur ba ltar
NK030(a)005:761: slob dpon bdag gis kyang 'jug cing dbang len no
NK030(a)005:762: // gnyis pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhugs cing dbang bskur ba la /
NK030(a)005:763: khrus dag ba dri dang lus 'bul dang //
NK030(a)005:764: bgegs bskrad lhar rlabs dam tshig spyin //
NK030(a)005:765: de nyid dbog dang chu nan dang //
NK030(a)005:766: bsgrags dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK030(a)005:767: lha dbab ba dang nan tan dang //
NK030(a)005:768: spyan dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK030(a)005:771: bcu drug dang po khrus ni /
NK030(a)005:773: las bum gyis slob ma rnams bkru zhing //
NK030(a)005:774: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyi ni sogs kyis lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig pa dag nas //
NK030(a)005:775: lus shel gong phyis pa ltar bsgoms shig /
NK030(a)005:776: gnyis pa mig dar dgab pa ni /
NK030(a)005:777: dar dmar pos mig dgab la /
NK030(a)005:778: de snga phan chad dkyil 'khor mi mthong ba'i barda'o //
NK030(a)005:780: bla mas bu dga' ci la dga' /
NK030(a)005:782: / bu khyod spro ba ci la spro //
NK030(a)005:784: slob mas bdag ni tshe dpag med pa yi //
NK030(a)005:785: dkyil 'khor bzhugs cing dbang zhu spro //
NK030(a)005:788: rgyal thebs kyis slob ma dkyil 'khor gyi lho sgo'i nang phyogs su khrid de /
NK030(a)005:789: phyag 'tshal zhing lus 'bul bar bsam la //
NK030(a)005:790: dkyil 'khor grong khyer dam pa'i sa //
NK030(a)005:791: lho'i phyogs su brten nas ni //
NK030(a)005:792: sku'i dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)005:794: nub sgo'i nang du khrid la //
NK030(a)005:795: dkyil 'khor dam pa grong khyer gyis //
NK030(a)005:796: nub kyi phyogs su brten nas ni //
NK030(a)005:797: gsung gi dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)005:799: byang sgo'i nang du khrid la //
NK030(a)005:800: dkyil 'khor dam pa'i grong khyer gyis //
NK030(a)005:801: byang gi phyogs su brten nas ni /
NK030(a)005:803: / 'phrin las dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)005:806: dkyil 'khor dam pa grong khyer gyis //
NK030(a)005:807: shar gyis phyogs su brten nas ni //
NK030(a)005:808: thugs kyi dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)005:810: lnga pa bgegs bskrad pa ni //
NK030(a)005:811: slob ma la yungs dkar gtor zhing bgegs bskrad par bsam la //
NK030(a)005:812: h+r+aiihpad+ma ta kri ta badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+h+ri wa hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK030(a)005:814: drug pa lhar brlabs pa ni /
NK030(a)005:816: / 'od khyed rang rnams tshe dpag tu med pa //
NK030(a)005:817: sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa re
NK030(a)005:818: re gsal ba'i spyi bo dkar po mgrin par +aahdamara
NK030(a)005:819: po // thugs kar h+aum sngon po re rer bsgoms
NK030(a)005:820: gnas gsum du dri bzang gi thig le re re
NK030(a)005:821: po // byed do // bdun pa dam tshig sbyin pa ni //
NK030(a)005:824: gsang sngags theg pa 'dir bzhugs na //
NK030(a)005:825: dam med 'di phyi gnyis khar lhung //
NK030(a)005:826: dam tshig tshul bzhin bsrungs nus sam //
NK030(a)005:828: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig ni //
NK030(a)005:829: ma grub bar du ma ltung na //
NK030(a)005:830: yang nas yang du bcas pa bzhin //
NK030(a)005:831: lus dang srog la babs kyang bsrungs //
NK030(a)005:833: brgyad pa dam tshig dbog ba ni //
NK030(a)005:834: snying khar rdo rje bzung la //
NK030(a)005:835: dus gsum bde gshegs rnams kyi snying po ni /
NK030(a)005:837: / 'das dang ma byung da ltar gsum gyi lha //
NK030(a)005:838: rnal 'byor pa'i bsnyen cing bsgrub pa 'di //
NK030(a)005:839: da lta nyid du khyod la 'bogs par bya //
NK030(a)005:840: badz+ra sarba sa ma ya h+aum //
NK030(a)005:841: dgu pa dam chu blud pa ni //
NK030(a)005:842: bdud rtsi lce la bzhag la /
NK030(a)005:845: skal ldan khyod kyis gsang ba'i mchog /
NK030(a)005:846: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i /
NK030(a)005:847: bdag gi bka' la ma 'da' bsrungs //
NK030(a)005:848: i tan ti na ra kan /
NK030(a)005:849: yang de ring phyin chad bu khyod kyis //
NK030(a)005:850: gsang cher nga yin brnyas pa spongs //
NK030(a)005:851: brnyas na sangs rgyas kun brnyas pas //
NK030(a)005:852: tshe'i dus byas dmyal bar skye //
NK030(a)005:854: bcu pa dam tshig bsgrag pa ni //
NK030(a)005:855: bu khyod bla med sems kyi sangs rgyas rigs //
NK030(a)005:856: sangs rgyas lha'i sa la gnas gyur gyi //
NK030(a)005:857: mos pas zhugs la bla med sgrubs pa'i phyir //
NK030(a)005:858: rgyal ba'i dam tshig gnyis med sems kyi spyod //
NK030(a)005:860: bcu gcig pa me tog dor ba ni //
NK030(a)005:861: me tog cod pan thal mo'i bar du gzung la /
NK030(a)005:864: tshe dpag med pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)005:865: rin chen byang chub sems kyi me tog 'di //
NK030(a)005:866: sku gsung thugs kyi dbyibs su bdag 'bul na //
NK030(a)005:867: dngos grub rnam gsum bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:869: ces dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su gtad cing 'phang ngo //
NK030(a)005:870: bcu gnyis pa lha dbab ni /
NK030(a)005:872: me tog phog pa'i lha dbyer med gnas gsum du gtugs la /
NK030(a)005:873: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)005:874: me tog dor ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)005:875: sku gsung thugs la thim nas kyang /
NK030(a)005:876: dngos grub rnams gsum khyod la sbyin //
NK030(a)005:877: ka ya wa k+ka tsit+ta sid+d+hii h+aum /
NK030(a)005:878: bcu gsum pa lha bsgoms par nan tan bya ba ni /
NK030(a)005:880: kye dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i gsang mtshan btags //
NK030(a)005:881: mo thams cad kun tu bzang mo la sogs pa'i gsang mtshan btags la /
NK030(a)005:883: / 'o khyeer rang rnams kyi me tog phog pa'i lha mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa yin pas //
NK030(a)005:884: lha tshogs rnams kyi sku snang la rang bzhin med pa //
NK030(a)005:885: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan bzhin du bsgom zhing bsgrub pa la nan tan mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:886: bcu bzhi pa spyan dbye ba ni //
NK030(a)005:887: thur mas spyan dar bsal la //
NK030(a)005:889: bu khyod kyi ni shes pa yi //
NK030(a)005:890: ma rig mig gis ling tog rnams //
NK030(a)005:891: bde gshegs dgongs pas gsal bar bgyi //
NK030(a)005:893: bco lnga pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni //
NK030(a)005:895: ho dkyil 'khor lha tshogs 'di la ltos //
NK030(a)005:896: sngon chad ma brnyed de ring rnyed //
NK030(a)005:897: sngags dang phyag rgya'i dngos grub thob //
NK030(a)005:898: rtag tu dam tshig thub par bsrungs /
NK030(a)005:899: 'o rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor mthong ba tsam gyis //
NK030(a)005:900: skye ba bdun tshun chod du /
NK030(a)005:901: ma bsgom kyang sangs rgyas thob pa la sogs pa phan yon du ma yod do //
NK030(a)005:902: bcu drug pa tshogs mchod yon 'bul ba ni //
NK030(a)005:903: tshogs mchod rgyas bsdus ci rigs pa byas shing //
NK030(a)005:904: lha tshogs dang mi la byas shing //
NK030(a)005:905: lha tshogs dang mi la 'bul lo //
NK030(a)005:906: yon ni ci 'byor pa'i yon phul la //
NK030(a)005:907: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus /
NK030(a)005:908: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK030(a)005:910: rtag du thugs rjes gzung du gsol /
NK030(a)005:912: de ltar dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK030(a)005:913: las dang po ba bzhugs yin kyang /
NK030(a)005:915: / 'og min du thar lam pa zhugs pa dang bskal ba mnyams pa'i yon tan no //
NK030(a)005:916: dbang gi dngos gzhi la gsum gyi dang po sngon 'gro ni //
NK030(a)005:918: gsol ba gdab pa'i rjes bzlos mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:919: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:920: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas kyi /
NK030(a)005:921: rdo rje tshe dbang rin po che //
NK030(a)005:922: deng 'dir bdag la bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:924: de nas slob dpon gyi dbu brgyan la sogs pa'i chas gos rnams brnab /
NK030(a)005:925: bum pa phyag tu thogs la /
NK030(a)005:926: 'o khyed rang rnams dmigs pa 'di bzhin du mdzod //
NK030(a)005:927: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer spros //
NK030(a)005:928: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgya la phog /
NK030(a)005:929: de yang chos kyi sku rnams gzugs kyi skur bzhengs //
NK030(a)005:930: gzugs kyi sku rnams yang mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa 'khor bcas kyi skur bzhengs nas /
NK030(a)005:931: mdun bskyed dang gnyis su med par nam mkhar sgom la //
NK030(a)005:932: de yang tshe dpag med la sogs rigs lngas bkra shis pa'i dgongs pa mdzad /
NK030(a)005:933: sangs rgyas spyan ma la sogs yum lngas //
NK030(a)005:934: rin po che'i bum pa byang chub sems kyis chus
NK030(a)005:935: gang ba thogs nas dbang bskur tshe'i lha mo dang
NK030(a)005:936: dbyings kyi lha mos bkra shis brjod cing glu len
NK030(a)005:937: / khro bo bcus bar chad kyi bgegs bskrad //
NK030(a)005:938: sgo ma bzhi phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul bar bsgom mdzod //
NK030(a)005:939: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba gser gyi ri bo 'dra //
NK030(a)005:942: rdzogs sangs rgyas nas da lta'i bar //
NK030(a)005:943: bum pa gcig nas gcig byo dang //
NK030(a)005:944: mar me gcig nas gcig spar ltar //
NK030(a)005:945: dus rgyun chad med pa'i bkra shis brjod //
NK030(a)005:948: gsang ba'i dbang gi dod dang /
NK030(a)005:949: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi dod dang /
NK030(a)005:950: dbang bzhi pa tshig dbang rin po che de'i dod do //
NK030(a)005:952: dmigs pa bsam rgyud gong bzhin la bsgrag tshig ni //
NK030(a)005:953: rin chen sna tshogs rgyu las byung //
NK030(a)005:954: kha dog dbyibs su ldan pa yis //
NK030(a)005:955: shes rab yum gyis bum pa 'dis //
NK030(a)005:956: spyi bo'i gtsug tu dbang bskur ba //
NK030(a)005:957: dbang mchog dam pa thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:958: badz+ra ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:960: bum pa'i chus dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:961: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib dag par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:962: tshe dpag med yab yum gyi tsa ka li spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)005:963: 'o bde ba can dang mdun bskyed dang /
NK030(a)005:964: bla ma'i thugs ka nas tshe dpag med yab yum byon nas /
NK030(a)005:965: 'chi med tshe yi bdud rtsis bkang ba'i bum pas
NK030(a)005:966: spyi bo nas dbang bskur bas thugs kar thim par
NK030(a)005:967: bsgoms mdzod cig / bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK030(a)005:968: thugs rje'i sku mchog yon tan rgya mtsho'i gter //
NK030(a)005:969: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi gzhal yas nas //
NK030(a)005:970: rdo rje tshe'i lha mo ye shes g.yung drung dpal gyis sku //
NK030(a)005:971: byang chub bde mchog rol pa thabs kyi gtso //
NK030(a)005:972: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:973: byang chub sems kyi ye shes bdud rtsi 'dis //
NK030(a)005:974: skal ldan rnams la tshe yis dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:975: a yu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum /
NK030(a)005:976: tshe b+h+r+aum n+ri dzaha b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:977: gtso bo yab yum kyi sku las sprul ba'i lha mo bzhi'i sku sbyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)005:980: bla ma'i thugs ka nas byung pa'i sprul pa'i lha
NK030(a)005:981: mor bzhis 'chi med bdud rtsis gang pa'i bum pa
NK030(a)005:983: lha mo bzhi thugs kar thim par bsgom mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:984: h+aum 'gro ba yongs la tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)005:985: dkar mo 'gyogs byed zhi ba'i las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)005:986: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)005:987: rdo rje tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)005:988: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:989: h+aum 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)005:990: ser mo 'gyogs byed rgyas pa'i las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)005:991: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)005:992: rin chen tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)005:993: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:994: h+aum 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)005:995: dmar mo 'gyogs byed dbang gi las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)005:996: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)005:997: pad+ma tshe mchog thob pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)005:999: h+aum 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK030(a)005:1000: ljang mo 'gyogs byed drag po'i las byed tshogs //
NK030(a)005:1001: tshe dang gzi brjid 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)005:1002: las kyi tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)005:1004: tshe'i lha mo bzhi'i sku spyi bor bzhags la /
NK030(a)005:1006: bla ma'i thugs ka nas byung ba'i tshe'i lha mo bzhi /
NK030(a)005:1008: / 'chi med tshe'i bdud rtsis gang ba'i bum ba spyi bor nas dbang bskur /
NK030(a)005:1009: tshe'i lha mo bzhi thugs kar thim par bsgoms mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:1010: h+aum shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)005:1012: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1014: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)005:1015: +aahyu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1017: lho phyogs 'khor lo rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)005:1019: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1021: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)005:1022: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1023: h+aum nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)005:1025: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1028: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK030(a)005:1029: h+aum byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)005:1031: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1033: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob bar shog /
NK030(a)005:1034: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1035: dbyings kyi lha mo bzhi'i sku spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)005:1039: bla ma'i thugs ka nas byung ba'i dbyings kyi lha
NK030(a)005:1040: mo bzhis 'chi med bdud rtsis gang ba'i bum pa
NK030(a)005:1042: dbyings kyi lha mo bzhi thugs kar thim par sgom mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:1043: h+aum rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1044: lha mo dkar mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)005:1045: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1047: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)005:1048: +aahyu b+hi du dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum rin chen dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1049: lha mo ser mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)005:1050: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1052: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)005:1054: h+aum pad+ma dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1055: lha mo dmar mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)005:1056: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1058: / 'chi med tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)005:1059: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1060: h+aum las kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor nas /
NK030(a)005:1061: lha mo ljang mo gzi brjid 'bar //
NK030(a)005:1062: skal ldan rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1064: / 'chi med rig 'dzin tshe dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)005:1066: khro bo bcu'i sku spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)005:1069: bla ma'i thugs ka nas byon pa'i /
NK030(a)005:1070: khro bo bcu'i phyag nas 'chi med tshe'i bdud rtsis
NK030(a)005:1071: gang ba'i bum pa thogs nas spyi bo nas dbang
NK030(a)005:1072: bskur / khro bo bcu'i thugs kar thim par sgom mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:1073: h+aum shar phyogs 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)005:1074: khro bo chen po rnam par rgyal ba yis //
NK030(a)005:1075: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1077: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)005:1078: +aa yu b+hi ti dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sa ma ye h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1080: h+aum shar lho 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas /
NK030(a)005:1081: khro bo chen po dbyug pa sngon po yis //
NK030(a)005:1082: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1084: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)005:1086: h+aum lho phyogs 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs steng nas //
NK030(a)005:1087: khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed po yis //
NK030(a)005:1088: skal ldan bu mchog rnam la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1090: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)005:1092: h+aum lho nub 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas /
NK030(a)005:1093: khro bo chen po mi g.yo mgon po yis //
NK030(a)005:1094: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1096: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)005:1097: a yu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1098: h+aum nub phyogs 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)005:1099: khro bo chen po rta mgrin rgyal po yis /
NK030(a)005:1100: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1102: / 'chi ba med pa'i tshe dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)005:1104: h+aum nub byang 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)005:1105: khro bo chen po gzhan gyis mi thub pa /
NK030(a)005:1106: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1108: / 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)005:1110: h+aum byang phyogs 'khor lo dkar po'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK030(a)005:1111: khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yis //
NK030(a)005:1112: skal ldan bu mchog rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)005:1114: / 'chi ba med pa tshe yi dbang thob shog /

NK030(a)005:1479: phyag mtshan 'khor lo la sogs pa lnga spyi bor bzhag la /
NK030(a)005:1480: skyod pas mi thub mi g.yo la sogs dang //
NK030(a)005:1481: phyag mtshan rdo rje lta bur byin brlabs pas /
NK030(a)005:1483: / 'chi med rdo rje lta bur 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)005:1486: bskyod pas mi thub mi g.yo zhes sogs dang //
NK030(a)005:1487: tshe nas ye shes lha tshogs lta bur byin rlabs pas //
NK030(a)005:1488: mi nub rgyal mtshan lta bur 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)005:1491: spyod pa mi thub la sogs dang //
NK030(a)005:1493: bskyod pas tshe zan 'byung ba lnga ru byin rlabs pas //
NK030(a)005:1494: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su grub par shog /
NK030(a)005:1497: skyood pas mi thub sogs dang //
NK030(a)005:1498: tshe 'bras ye shes lnga ru byin rlabs pas //
NK030(a)005:1499: rig lnga'i sangs rgyas lnga ru 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)005:1502: skyood pa mi thub mi g.yo tshe'i rang bzhin la sogs dang /
NK030(a)005:1503: tshe chang bdud rtsi lta bur byin rlabs pas /
NK030(a)005:1504: 'gyur med byang chub sems su 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)005:1506: bkra shis rdzas brgyad spyi'am bye brag tu 'grim la /
NK030(a)005:1507: bskyood pas mi thub mi g.yo la sogs dang //
NK030(a)005:1508: yo byad bkra shis rdzas su byin rlabs pas //
NK030(a)005:1509: bkra shis lha mo brgyad du 'grub par shog /
NK030(a)005:1510: na mo de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK030(a)005:1512: de dag rgyas par byed na //
NK030(a)005:1513: bkra shis rdzas brgyad las sngags kyi gsang la //
NK030(a)005:1515: dang po yungs dkar sbyin la /
NK030(a)005:1516: sngon bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)005:1517: gsang sngags rigs sngags bdag po phyag na rdo rjes /
NK030(a)005:1518: sgrub pa'i rdzas brgyad yungs dkar phyag du phul te /
NK030(a)005:1519: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa /
NK030(a)005:1522: yungs dkar du rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1523: yungs dkar rdo rje'i rigs te thams cad du //
NK030(a)005:1524: bgegs rnams ma lus dag par byed pa ste //
NK030(a)005:1525: mthu stobs yon tan phun sum tshogs pa yis //
NK030(a)005:1526: bkra shis des kyang bgegs rnams zhi byed shog /
NK030(a)005:1529: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)005:1530: r+ts+wa 'tshong gi khye'u bkra shis kyi r+ts+wa dur ba phyag tu phul te //
NK030(a)005:1531: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa //
NK030(a)005:1534: dur wa'i rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1535: dur bas tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste //
NK030(a)005:1536: rdo rje sems dpa' tshe ni rab bsgrub phyir //
NK030(a)005:1537: nyon mongs skye shi rgyun chad gyur pa yis //
NK030(a)005:1538: bkra shis des kyang tshe ni 'phel bar shog /
NK030(a)005:1541: shing thog bil ba gtad la /
NK030(a)005:1542: sngon bcom ldan 'das shwakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)005:1543: lha tshangs pas shing thog bil ba phyag tu phul te //
NK030(a)005:1544: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis brlabs pa de bzhin //
NK030(a)005:1546: bil ba rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1547: bil bas rgyu rkyen 'bras ldan pa yis /
NK030(a)005:1549: / 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa rnams //
NK030(a)005:1550: snying rje byang chub mchog tu dag gyur bas //
NK030(a)005:1551: bkra shis des kyang don kun grub par shog /
NK030(a)005:1552: bil ba a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK030(a)005:1553: g+hi wam phyag du gtad la /
NK030(a)005:1554: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)005:1555: glang po che nor skyong gi bus //
NK030(a)005:1556: g+hi wam phyag du phul ba ste //
NK030(a)005:1557: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis brlabs pa de bzhin du /
NK030(a)005:1559: g+hi wam gi rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1560: g+hi wam dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi sman //
NK030(a)005:1561: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur nas //
NK030(a)005:1562: nyon mongs zung ngu med par gyur pa yis //
NK030(a)005:1563: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal zhi gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1564: g+hi wam a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1566: sngon bcom ldan nas sh+aakya thub pa la //
NK030(a)005:1567: bram ze skal rgyal gyi bus /
NK030(a)005:1568: sman li khri phyag tu phul te //
NK030(a)005:1569: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis brlabs pa de bzhin du /
NK030(a)005:1571: li khri rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1572: li khri dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin te //
NK030(a)005:1573: chos rnams ma lus yongs su gyur nas kyang //
NK030(a)005:1574: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur pa'i //
NK030(a)005:1575: bkra shis des kyang rgyal srid brtan gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1576: li khri a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1578: sngon gcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la /
NK030(a)005:1579: zhing pa'i bu mo legs skyes mas //
NK030(a)005:1581: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa de bzhin du //
NK030(a)005:1583: zho'i rdzas kyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1584: zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa yis //
NK030(a)005:1585: snying po chos nyid ye shes rnams rtogs nas //
NK030(a)005:1586: yon tan kun gyi dbyings su gyur ba yis //
NK030(a)005:1587: bkra shis des kyang dug gsum zhi byed shog /
NK030(a)005:1588: d+ha ra ti ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1590: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la /
NK030(a)005:1591: gzugs kyi lha mo 'od 'chang mas me long phyag du phul te /
NK030(a)005:1592: bkra shis pa'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa de bzhin du /
NK030(a)005:1594: me long gi rdzas kyis bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1595: me long ye shes rgya mtsho chen po yis //
NK030(a)005:1596: ye shes rgya mtsho mchog tu dag gyur ste //
NK030(a)005:1597: rnam dag chos la thogs med lung ston pa'i //
NK030(a)005:1598: bkra shis des kyang sgribs pa dag gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1599: a dar sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)005:1601: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la /
NK030(a)005:1602: lha'i dbang po brgya sbyin gyis /
NK030(a)005:1603: dung g.yas su 'khyil ba phyag du phul ste //
NK030(a)005:1604: bkra shis ba'i rdzas su byin gyis rlabs pa de bzhin du //
NK030(a)005:1605: deng 'dir slob ma 'di rnams la dung gi rdzas kyis bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1606: dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i tshul //
NK030(a)005:1607: ye shes rgya mtsho nyid du dag gyur te //
NK030(a)005:1608: chos rnams ma nor yongs su ston pa yi //
NK030(a)005:1609: bkra shis des kyang tshig dbang thob par shog /
NK030(a)005:1612: na mo de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang sogs bardzoda do //
NK030(a)005:1613: des shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob /
NK030(a)005:1615: rdzogs rim bde stong bsgoms pa la dbang /
NK030(a)005:1616: mthar thug chos kyi sku thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1619: de kho na nyid kyis dbang bskur ba ni /
NK030(a)005:1620: phyi snod kyi rang bzhin 'od du zhu nas //
NK030(a)005:1621: nang bcud kyi sems can la thim /
NK030(a)005:1622: nang bcud kyi sems can 'od du zhu nas /
NK030(a)005:1624: khyed rang rnams kyang 'od du zhu nas mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du dar gcig bsgom /
NK030(a)005:1625: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i dbyings nyid la /
NK030(a)005:1626: rnal 'byor a yu dmar pos tshe sbas pas /
NK030(a)005:1627: de las phyag rgya bdun gyis brgyas ni gdab bar bya /
NK030(a)005:1628: dang po sku mchog nyid kyi rgya //
NK030(a)005:1629: gnyis pa thabs dang shes rab rgya //
NK030(a)005:1630: gsum pa sku gsung thugs kyi rgya //
NK030(a)005:1631: bzhi pa ye shes lnga'i rgya //
NK030(a)005:1632: lnga pa gser gyi 'khor lo'i rgya //
NK030(a)005:1633: drug pa rta mchog dbang gi rgya //
NK030(a)005:1634: bdun pa chos nyid dbyings kyi rgya //
NK030(a)005:1635: chos nyid dbyings su tshe spas pas //
NK030(a)005:1636: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgrar langs kyang //
NK030(a)005:1637: de la gzung zhing gcad du med //
NK030(a)005:1638: brgyas 'debs mas ni rgyas gdabs pas //
NK030(a)005:1639: bran gyis 'gal bar mi byed cing //
NK030(a)005:1640: bde ba mos ni tshe bsrung bas //
NK030(a)005:1641: bdud dang mu ge gang gis kyang /
NK030(a)005:1643: / 'di la gnod par mi nus so //
NK030(a)005:1644: gsang ba mos ni tshe spas pas //
NK030(a)005:1645: mi shor bas ni dam du bsdoms //
NK030(a)005:1646: tshe 'phel mas ni tshe bsrungs bas //
NK030(a)005:1648: na mo b+ha ga wa te a pa ra mi ta /
NK030(a)005:1650: su b+hi ni tsi ta te dz+wa ra tsa ya /
NK030(a)005:1652: ar+ha ha te sam mya k+sam bud+d+ha ya /
NK030(a)005:1658: a pa ra mi ta pu pun+yee /
NK030(a)005:1659: dz+ny+aa na sam b+ha ro pa tsi te /
NK030(a)005:1660: sarba sam ska ri pa ri shu d+ha /
NK030(a)005:1662: sa mud ga te swa b+ha wa b+hi shud d+he
NK030(a)005:1663: ma h+aa ya na ba ri wa re s+w+aa h+aa
NK030(a)005:1664: / zhes man+dala dang bsngo ba smon lam bkra shis brjod //
NK030(a)005:1665: des dbang bzhi pa de kho na nyid tshig dbang rin po che thob //
NK030(a)005:1666: sgo gsum tha dad du 'dzin ba'i sgribs pa dag /
NK030(a)005:1667: rdzogs rim phyag rgya chen po sgom pa la dbang //
NK030(a)005:1668: mthar thug ngo bo nyid kyi sku thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1670: de'i gong du shes rab ye shes //
NK030(a)005:1673: de bzhis dngos gzhi de song nas /
NK030(a)005:1675: de nas mchod pa gong bzhin byed //
NK030(a)005:1676: bsngo ba smon lam spyi dang mthun par bya //
NK030(a)005:1677: gang yang bdag blo gti mug sogs kyis nyes pa bzod par gsol //
NK030(a)005:1678: khyed kyi sems can don kun mdzad //
NK030(a)005:1681: mdun bskyed kyi ye shes pa gshegs //
NK030(a)005:1682: dam tshig pa rang la bsdu //
NK030(a)005:1684: tshe dang ye shes rgya mtsho'i gter /
NK030(a)005:1686: / 'od dpag med pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)005:1687: ye shes bzhi'i rang bzhin can /
NK030(a)005:1688: rigs kyi yum bzhi'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)005:1689: gsang ba yum gyi lha mo bzhi //
NK030(a)005:1690: dbyings kyi lha mo'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)005:1691: mi dge bcu po tshar gcod phyir //
NK030(a)005:1692: khro bo bcu yis bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)005:1693: zhi rgyas dbang drag rang bzhin can //
NK030(a)005:1694: sgo ma bzhi'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)005:1695: dngos grub ma lus bstsol ba yi //
NK030(a)005:1696: rdo rje lha mo'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)005:1700: de nas rdul tshon bsdus la chu chen nang du dor ro //
NK030(a)005:1701: bdag bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor rim pa bzhin du bsdu //
NK030(a)005:1703: slar tshe dpag med du gsal bas spyod lam bya'o //
NK030(a)005:1704: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med pa yis //
NK030(a)005:1705: thugs kyi dgongs pa rgyud sde'i don rnams rdzogs //
NK030(a)005:1706: thugs rje'i chu rgyun rim par legs brgyud nas //
NK030(a)005:1707: bdag nyid smin cing grol ba'i byin rlabs ni //
NK030(a)005:1708: tshe bsgrub dbang mchog bdud rtsi'i char rgyun gyi //
NK030(a)005:1709: gdul bya las dang skal ba ldan pa rnams //
NK030(a)005:1710: tshe dpal bsod nams rgya chen rgyas par byas //
NK030(a)005:1711: legs bshad 'di ni rdo rje bzang po yis //
NK030(a)005:1712: gnas mchog bsgrub sde bzang po mngon dga' ru /
NK030(a)005:1713: bris pa'i dge bas phan thog dar rgyas shog /
NK030(a)005:1718: / / / bkra shis dpal 'bar 'dzam gling brgyan gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:1719: des 'chi med tshe'i dngos grub len pa de song nas //
NK030(a)005:1720: gnyis pa dam rdzas la brten nas sku gsung thugs
NK030(a)005:1721: yon tan 'phrin las kyi dngos grub len pa ni
NK030(a)005:1723: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub kyi //
NK030(a)005:1724: gzugs zan la gzo zhing mar gyi brgyan cha can dang /
NK030(a)005:1726: la sogs dngos grub kyi rdzas sna tshogs //
NK030(a)005:1728: btung ba'i rigs sna tshogs bshams la //
NK030(a)005:1730: 'dus pa mdo'i lha tshogs la sogs bsgom la mchod bstod bya zhing /
NK030(a)005:1732: nye bsnyen gyi sgrub pa dang /
NK030(a)005:1733: bsgrub pa chen po'i sgo nas bzlas brjod kyi //
NK030(a)005:1734: bsnyen pa brgya 'am stong la sogs 'bul gzungs thag
NK030(a)005:1735: la brten nas dngos grub kyi dmigs pa'i 'phro 'dus
NK030(a)005:1741: kar ma sid+d+hi ha ha la bsnyen no //
NK030(a)005:1743: h+aum chos nyid bde ba chen po'i skur byung ba //
NK030(a)005:1744: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)005:1745: dur khrod dregs pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa'i //
NK030(a)005:1746: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)005:1747: ye shes 'bar ba brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1748: ko ri khro mo brgyad kyis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1749: chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1750: sing ha phra med brgyad kyis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1751: tshad med bzhi rdzogs gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1752: rta gdong sgo ma tshogs bcas dngos grub bstsol /
NK030(a)005:1754: / 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod nang ga shed nas //
NK030(a)005:1755: spor ma gsang yum tshogs bcas dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)005:1756: dam tshig lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1757: dbang phyug ma sring tshogs kyis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1758: dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1759: mkha' gro sum bcu rtsa gnyis dngos grub bstsol /
NK030(a)005:1761: / 'phrin las myur 'gyogs chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1762: ma bdun sring mo bzhi yis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1763: sgrol byed 'bar ba'i chen pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1764: rdo rje ging chen bac+wo brgyad dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1765: zhing chen 'bar ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1766: khro rgyal yab yum drug bcus dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1767: ci bgyis bka' nyan las kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1768: pho nya drug bcu rtsa bzhis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1769: las rnams yongs su gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1770: ma mo drug bcu'i tshogs kyis dngos grub stsol //
NK030(a)005:1771: sdom pa'i sa la gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)005:1772: rig 'dzin rtsal chang tshogs kyis dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1773: gnas mchog yang dag don gyi 'og min nas //
NK030(a)005:1774: rgyal ba kun bzang yab yum dngos grub bstsol /
NK030(a)005:1776: / 'og min dbang phyug chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK030(a)005:1777: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK030(a)005:1778: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs lnga yum dang bcas //
NK030(a)005:1779: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku yi dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1780: lha klu gnod sbyin so so'i gnas mchog nas //
NK030(a)005:1781: bacomaldana rigs gsum mgon pos dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)005:1782: o rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug tu /
NK030(a)005:1783: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs sprul dga' rdor dang //
NK030(a)005:1784: rgyal po'i bu mo rin chen gsal sgron la //
NK030(a)005:1785: rdo rje sems dang gsang bdag dngos byon nas //
NK030(a)005:1786: dbang bzhi rdzogs bskur rtogs tshogs lha ngo sprad //
NK030(a)005:1787: dbang rtags chags shing me long rnam gnyis sbyin //
NK030(a)005:1788: rig 'dzin khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas nas //
NK030(a)005:1789: de'i dngos grub dam pa cha gcig kyang //
NK030(a)005:1790: de ring gsang ba'i gnas mchog chen po 'dir //
NK030(a)005:1791: bsgrub mchog skal ldan bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:1792: rgya gar yul gyi pha rol na //
NK030(a)005:1793: o rgyan yul gyi tshur mtshams na //
NK030(a)005:1794: ma ga ta'i brag phug tu //
NK030(a)005:1795: o rgyan rgyal po d+harma ka ya dang //
NK030(a)005:1796: klu'i rgyal po bu mo gnyis //
NK030(a)005:1797: dga' rab rdo rje spyan drangs nas //
NK030(a)005:1798: tshom bu stong gi dkyil 'khor bsgrubs //
NK030(a)005:1799: khri phrag gcig tu sangs rgyas pa //
NK030(a)005:1800: de'i dngos grub cha gcig kyang //
NK030(a)005:1801: de ring gsang ba'i gnas 'di ru //
NK030(a)005:1802: sgrub mchog bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:1803: rgya gar yul gyis mar mtshams na //
NK030(a)005:1804: za hor yul gyi yar mtshams su /
NK030(a)005:1806: rgyal po in+t+ra bo d+hi dang //
NK030(a)005:1807: sras mo ni lan d+ha ra gnyis //
NK030(a)005:1808: tshom bu lnga brgya'i dkyil 'khor bsgrubs //
NK030(a)005:1809: khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK030(a)005:1810: de'i dngos grub cha gcig kyang //
NK030(a)005:1811: de ring gsang ba'i gnas 'di ru //
NK030(a)005:1812: bsgrub mchog bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:1813: rgya gar yul gyi mar mtshams su //
NK030(a)005:1814: sing ga d+ha yi yar mtshams su //
NK030(a)005:1815: g.yu mtsho gling dgu'i brag phug tu //
NK030(a)005:1816: sing ha u pa ra tsa dang //
NK030(a)005:1817: sras mo mgo ma di byi gnyis //
NK030(a)005:1818: tshom bu lnga bcu'i dkyil 'khor bsgrubs //
NK030(a)005:1819: rgya phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK030(a)005:1820: de'i dngos grub cha gcig kyang //
NK030(a)005:1821: de ring gsang ba'i gnas 'di ru //
NK030(a)005:1822: bsgrub mchog bdag la bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:1823: rgya gar yul gyi dbus shod du //
NK030(a)005:1824: ba ra na s+ai'i gnas dag tu //
NK030(a)005:1825: dge slong nyi byed seng ge dang //
NK030(a)005:1826: srin po snams bu'i bu mo na shi gnyis //
NK030(a)005:1827: tshom bu gsum pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgrubs /
NK030(a)005:1829: / 'khor ni lnga brgya sangs rgyas te //
NK030(a)005:1830: de'i dngos grub cha gcig kyang //
