NK030(a)005:2181: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK030(a)005:2183: phar 'phros dpal gyi thugs ka nas //
NK030(a)005:2184: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub bstsol /
NK030(a)005:2190: kar+m+aa yab yum sngags la ru lu re re dang /
NK030(a)005:2191: g+hu h+ya re re gdags so //
NK030(a)005:2196: nan dbang drag shul bzhis bstod //
NK030(a)005:2198: ho bcom ldan rigs bzhi'i he ru ka yab yum
NK030(a)005:2199: la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni bdag cag
NK030(a)005:2200: rnal 'byor pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir
NK030(a)005:2201: 'tshogs pa rnams / shes bya'i chos thams cad la ces pa man chad 'agre'o //
NK030(a)005:2202: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin bya'o //
NK030(a)005:2203: de nas gsal shing rim pa gsum pa la lung
NK030(a)005:2204: gi he ru ka bzhi'i dngos grub blangs pa la'ang
NK030(a)005:2205: don drug gis ston pa'i dang po spyan drangs ba
NK030(a)005:2206: ni / pho brang gi mar me la lung gi he ru ka yab yum /
NK030(a)005:2207: mtshams bzhi'i rtsibs la bskyed pa de lta bu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs ste /
NK030(a)005:2208: raka sha sh+ri he ru ka /
NK030(a)005:2209: rak+sha kro ti sh+aa ri h+aum /
NK030(a)005:2210: ru lu g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na sa nu yab yum /
NK030(a)005:2220: gsal shing gsum pa la me sbar /
NK030(a)005:2222: / 'bar ba dang gnyis su med par byon par bsam /
NK030(a)005:2223: de nas gnyis pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK030(a)005:2224: lung gi he ru ka yab yum rnams la gtor ma /
NK030(a)005:2227: gsum pa bskul tshig dang 'dzab gnyis kyi dang po bskul ba ni /
NK030(a)005:2228: lung gi he ru ka'i thugs ka nas /
NK030(a)005:2229: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar //
NK030(a)005:2230: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK030(a)005:2231: g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od zer ni //
NK030(a)005:2232: phar 'phros pas ni thugs ka thims /
NK030(a)005:2233: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub gsol /
NK030(a)005:2239: ru lu re re dang gu h+ya re re spel gyis gdags so //
NK030(a)005:2241: h+aum spyor ba dam tshig gsang ba'i sgrol ma'i dbyings //
NK030(a)005:2242: log lta myang byed skye gnas reg bya 'joms /
NK030(a)005:2243: ga na nyams pa mtshan ma sgrol /
NK030(a)005:2244: lung gi khro rgyal tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2246: ho bcom ldan lung gi he ru ka yab yum
NK030(a)005:2247: gyi tshogs la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni
NK030(a)005:2248: / bdag cag rnal 'byor pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir 'tshogs pa rnams la /
NK030(a)005:2249: shes bya'i chos thams cad la zhes pa man chad gang gis shes so //
NK030(a)005:2250: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK030(a)005:2251: gsal shing gi rim pa bzhi pa la khro mo brgyad kyi dngos grub blangs pa la /
NK030(a)005:2252: drug gi dang po sbyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2253: mar me la khro mo brgyad bskyed pa /
NK030(a)005:2254: de lta bu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs ba ni /
NK030(a)005:2255: ke ri brgyad po'i rtsa sngags rdzogs pa ra brjod la /
NK030(a)005:2258: ru lu dang g+hu ya bzlas /
NK030(a)005:2260: ki ri brgyad kyi thugs ka'i /
NK030(a)005:2261: snying po'i g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od 'phros bas /
NK030(a)005:2266: ke'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni /
NK030(a)005:2267: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul pa'i drag shul can //
NK030(a)005:2268: sku mdog phyag rgya sna tshogs cir yang stod //
NK030(a)005:2269: ye shes khro mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2270: khro mo brgyad kyi dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)005:2271: zhes pa la sogs pa dang bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK030(a)005:2272: gsal shing gi rim pa lnga pa la phra men
NK030(a)005:2273: brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi'i dngos grub blangs la drug
NK030(a)005:2274: gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2275: pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams dang po la sing+ha brgyad dang /
NK030(a)005:2276: sgo ma bzhi bskyed pa lta bu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)005:2281: yang sgo ma bzhi'i rtsa sngags /
NK030(a)005:2282: badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dzah la sogs pa bzhi brjod /
NK030(a)005:2284: la sogs gsal shing lnga pa la me spar /
NK030(a)005:2285: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam /
NK030(a)005:2286: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum gyis dbul /
NK030(a)005:2289: sing ha phra med brgyad rnams dang //
NK030(a)005:2290: sgo ma bzhi'i thugs kha nas /
NK030(a)005:2291: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na' phar 'phros pas ni mchod /
NK030(a)005:2292: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos bzlas pa ni sing+ha brgyad po'i rtsa sngags dang //
NK030(a)005:2293: sgo ma bzhi'i rtsa sngags ru lu spel mar bzlas so //
NK030(a)005:2296: h+aum sing ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)005:2297: stag gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnams ni //
NK030(a)005:2298: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK030(a)005:2299: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi thub par bsrungs //
NK030(a)005:2300: sgo skyong khro mo bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2302: phra men brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)005:2303: shes bya'i chos zhes pa dang //
NK030(a)005:2304: drug pa bsdu ba gong bzhin no //
NK030(a)005:2305: gsal shing gi rim pa drug pa las /
NK030(a)005:2307: gsang yum bzhi'i dngos grub blangs pa la drug gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2308: pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams gnyis pa la bskyed pa ste /
NK030(a)005:2310: badz+ra a pra ti ha ar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK030(a)005:2311: a rag mo h+aum zhes pa brgyad dang /
NK030(a)005:2312: sh+ri badz+ra mud ka ra sha ra lu sh+ri badz+ra ra ga sha ra ya ya na ma /
NK030(a)005:2313: ru lu sh+ri badz+ra g+han d+ha pra dz+wa la ru lu /
NK030(a)005:2316: zhes brjod la gsal shing drug pa la me spar /
NK030(a)005:2317: 'od dang bcas de byon par bsam /
NK030(a)005:2318: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyi dbul /
NK030(a)005:2319: gsum pa la gnyis kyi bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)005:2320: spor byed chen mo brgyad rnams dang /
NK030(a)005:2321: gsang ba yum bzhi'i thugs ka nas /
NK030(a)005:2322: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar 'phros pas mchod /
NK030(a)005:2324: a rag mo h+aum zhes pa brgyad dang /
NK030(a)005:2326: g+hu h+ya spel ma bzlas so //
NK030(a)005:2328: h+aum chos nyid rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba'i //
NK030(a)005:2329: sna tshogs cir snang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' zhing //
NK030(a)005:2330: srid gsum zhing du sbyor bas g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK030(a)005:2331: spor byed chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2332: bar 'khyams de'i shar lho nub byang sgor //
NK030(a)005:2333: dgyes pa bskyed ba gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi //
NK030(a)005:2334: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs sna tshogs 'phro //
NK030(a)005:2335: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2337: ho spor ma chen mo brgyad dang bzhi la gsang
NK030(a)005:2338: ba'i yum chen po dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo
NK030(a)005:2340: drug pa bsdu ba la gong bzhin no //
NK030(a)005:2341: yang gsal shing gi rim bdun pa la dbang phyug
NK030(a)005:2342: ma nyer brgyad kyi dngos grub blangs pas don drug
NK030(a)005:2343: gi dang po spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2344: pho brang gi mar me bar 'khyam gsum pa la dbang mo bskyed pa de /
NK030(a)005:2345: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)005:2346: b+h+yo badz+ra ma nu rag sha si b+h+yo /
NK030(a)005:2347: la sogs pa'i rtsa sngags tshang par brjod la /
NK030(a)005:2350: zhes brjod la gsal shing bdun ba la me sbar /
NK030(a)005:2351: 'od zer dang bcas nas byon par bsam /
NK030(a)005:2352: gnyis pa mchod sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyis dbul /
NK030(a)005:2353: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)005:2354: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad thugs ka nas //
NK030(a)005:2355: snying po ru lu g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i 'od 'phros //
NK030(a)005:2356: phar 'phros dpal tshur 'dus bdag rtsa sngags nyer brgyad bzlas la //
NK030(a)005:2357: ru lu dang g+hu h+ya spel la bzlas so //
NK030(a)005:2359: h+aum srin mo la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK030(a)005:2360: dregs pa'i lha chen rnams kyi chung ma de //
NK030(a)005:2361: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par spyod //
NK030(a)005:2362: nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2364: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)005:2368: mkha' 'gro sum bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dngos grub blangs
NK030(a)005:2369: pa la drug gi dang po ni spyan drangs pa
NK030(a)005:2370: ni / pho brang gi mar me la /
NK030(a)005:2371: bar 'khyams bzhi'i mkha' 'gro ma sum cu so gnyis bskyed pa de /
NK030(a)005:2372: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)005:2373: e a ra li h+aum zhes pa so gnyis brjod /
NK030(a)005:2376: zhes brjod la gsal shing brgyad pa la mar me spar /
NK030(a)005:2377: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK030(a)005:2378: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum sngags /
NK030(a)005:2379: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)005:2380: mkha' 'gro so gnyis thugs ka nas /
NK030(a)005:2386: ru lu g+hu ya rnams spel la bzlas so //
NK030(a)005:2388: h+aum nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing /
NK030(a)005:2390: / 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK030(a)005:2391: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK030(a)005:2392: mkha' 'gro sum bcu gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2394: mkha' 'gro sum bcu gnyis la dngos grub gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)005:2397: gsal shing dgu ba la ma mo bdun dang sring mo bzhi'i dngos grub blangs la /
NK030(a)005:2398: drug gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2399: pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams lnga pa la ma mo bdun dang //
NK030(a)005:2400: sring mo bzhi bskyed nas yod pa de //
NK030(a)005:2401: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la //
NK030(a)005:2402: ma ma d+h+aa du h+aum bdun dang ru lu spel //
NK030(a)005:2403: badz+ra dun ting b+h+yo zhes pa bzhi dang ru lu spel la //
NK030(a)005:2404: badz+ra ang+gu sha dz+aa dz+aa zhes brjod la gsal shing dgu pa la me spar /
NK030(a)005:2405: 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK030(a)005:2406: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum pa bzlas pa'i bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)005:2407: ma bdun sring mo'i snying po ru lu g+hu h+ya /
NK030(a)005:2410: ma ma d+ha du h+aum bdun dang //
NK030(a)005:2411: ru lu badz+ra dun ting b+h+yo bzhi dang //
NK030(a)005:2412: ru lu spel la bzlas so //
NK030(a)005:2414: h+aum 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK030(a)005:2415: phyi 'khor 'dul zhing nang 'khor skyongs mdzad pa //
NK030(a)005:2416: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK030(a)005:2417: bgegs bsrungs ma mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2419: ma sring bzhi la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)005:2421: drug pa bsdu ba ni gong dang 'adre'o //
NK030(a)005:2422: gsal shing bcu pa la ging bac+wa brgyad kyi dngos
NK030(a)005:2423: grub blangs pa la drug gi dang po spyan drangs
NK030(a)005:2424: pa ni / pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams drug pa la ging bac+wa brgyad bskyed pa de /
NK030(a)005:2425: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)005:2426: king ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u dang /
NK030(a)005:2429: gsal shing rim pa bcu pa la me sbar /
NK030(a)005:2431: / 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK030(a)005:2432: gnyis pa mchod pa sman raka gtor /
NK030(a)005:2433: gsum pa bzlas pa'i bskul tshig ni //
NK030(a)005:2439: king ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu b+h+yo /
NK030(a)005:2443: h+aum khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bac+wa brgyad ni //
NK030(a)005:2444: srid gsum las la thogs med sgrol la brtson //
NK030(a)005:2445: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas rlags par byed //
NK030(a)005:2446: ging chen ging lcags tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2448: ging chen bac+wa brgyad la zhes pa dang //
NK030(a)005:2450: gsal shing gi rim pa bcu drug pa la //
NK030(a)005:2451: steng phyogs kyi khro bo khro mo drug bcu'i dngos
NK030(a)005:2452: grub blangs ba la drug gis spyan drangs ba ni
NK030(a)005:2453: // pho brang gi mar me'i 'khyams bdun pa la /
NK030(a)005:2454: khro bo khro mo drug bcu bskyed de /
NK030(a)005:2458: ru lu'i spel ba bcu drug bzla /
NK030(a)005:2460: zhes brjod la gsal shing bcu gcig pa la me spar /
NK030(a)005:2461: gnyis pa mchod pa sman raka gtor gsum sngags kyis mchod do /
NK030(a)005:2462: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig ni /
NK030(a)005:2463: khro bo khro mo drug bcu'i thugs kha nas /
NK030(a)005:2467: tshul 'dus kro d+ha kro ti h'u /
NK030(a)005:2471: bcom ldan h'u mdzad sa gsum brjid kyis gnon //
NK030(a)005:2472: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha'i lha /
NK030(a)005:2474: / 'jigs byed 'bar bas gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK030(a)005:2475: khro bo khro mo rnams la phyag mtshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2477: khro bo khro mo drug bcu la dngos grub ces pa dang //
NK030(a)005:2478: drug pa bsdu ba gong dang mthun no //
NK030(a)005:2479: gsal shing gi rim pa bcu gnyis pa la phyogs
NK030(a)005:2480: bzhi'i pho nya nyis ba rgya dang bzhi bcu dngos
NK030(a)005:2481: grub blangs pa la drug gis dang po spyan drangs
NK030(a)005:2482: pa ni / pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams brgyad pa la //
NK030(a)005:2483: shar du b+ha na b+ha na //
NK030(a)005:2484: ad+gu sha ja zhes pa drug bcus //
NK030(a)005:2485: dung gi pho nya drug bcu //
NK030(a)005:2486: lhor ha la ha la pa sha h+aum zhes pa drug cus //
NK030(a)005:2487: lcags dang gser gyi pho nya drug cu //
NK030(a)005:2488: nub phyogs su gardza gardza po ta bam //
NK030(a)005:2489: zhes bse'i pho nya drug cu //
NK030(a)005:2490: byang phyogs su pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de ho //
NK030(a)005:2491: zhes g.yu'i pho nya drug cu /
NK030(a)005:2492: badz+ra ad+gu sha dz+aa dz+aa zhes //
NK030(a)005:2493: lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs //
NK030(a)005:2494: gsal shing bcu gnyis pa la me spar /
NK030(a)005:2496: / 'od dang bcas nas byon par bsam //
NK030(a)005:2497: gnyis pa mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyi dbul //
NK030(a)005:2498: gsum pa bzlas pa la bskul tshig /
NK030(a)005:2499: sngags gnyis kyi bskul tshig brjod pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2500: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu'i thugs ka nas //
NK030(a)005:2501: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na'i /
NK030(a)005:2504: b+ha na b+ha na ad+gu sha dza /
NK030(a)005:2506: ha la ha la pa sha h+aum ru lu /
NK030(a)005:2508: ru lu pa tsa pa tsa gan+de ho /
NK030(a)005:2511: h+aum ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yis /
NK030(a)005:2512: gdon bgegs 'dul ba'i las la thogs pa med /
NK030(a)005:2513: ci bgyis bka' nyan las rnams myur mdzad pa'i /
NK030(a)005:2514: phyogs bzhi pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2516: phyogs bzhi'i pho nya gnyis brgya bzhi bcu la dngos grub du gsol ba'i zhes la sogs pa dang /
NK030(a)005:2518: gsal shing gi rim pa bcu gsum pa la 'og
NK030(a)005:2519: phyogs kyi ma mo drug bcu'i dngos grub blangs la
NK030(a)005:2520: drug gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2521: pho brang gi mar me'i bar khyams dgu pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2522: ma mo shwa ra h+aum zhes /
NK030(a)005:2523: ma mo drug bcu bskyed pa de //
NK030(a)005:2525: zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs //
NK030(a)005:2526: gsal shing bcu gsum pa la me sbar /
NK030(a)005:2528: / 'od dang bcas nas gsal shing rtser byon par bsam //
NK030(a)005:2529: gnyis sman rag gtor gsum sngags kyi dbul //
NK030(a)005:2530: gsum pa bzlas pa la gnyis kyi dang po bskul tshig brjod pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2531: ma mo drug bcu'i thugs ka nas /
NK030(a)005:2532: snying po ru lu g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na'i /
NK030(a)005:2536: ru lu g+hu ya bzhi pa bstod pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2537: h+aum stong khams yongs su las la dbang ba yi //
NK030(a)005:2538: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyi bdag /
NK030(a)005:2539: yum chen las la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK030(a)005:2540: ma mo drug bcu'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK030(a)005:2542: 'og phyogs kyi ma mo drug bcu la dngos grub du gsol ba ni /
NK030(a)005:2543: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK030(a)005:2545: de nas gsal shing rim pa bcu bzhi pa la
NK030(a)005:2546: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi dngos grub blangs pa la'ang
NK030(a)005:2547: don drug gi dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2548: pho brang gi mar me'i bar 'khyams bcu pa na //
NK030(a)005:2549: ma h+aa g+hu ru shwa ri ram //
NK030(a)005:2551: yo ki ni gu ru sa ma ye dzah zhes
NK030(a)005:2552: rig 'dzin rig pa 'dzin tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab
NK030(a)005:2554: gsal shing gi rim bcu bzhi pa la /
NK030(a)005:2556: zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la spyan 'dren /
NK030(a)005:2557: gsal shing bcu bzhi pa la me sbar /
NK030(a)005:2558: 'od dang bcas nas gsal zhing gi rtse la byon par bsam /
NK030(a)005:2561: ma h+aa pany+tsa a smri ta kha hi /
NK030(a)005:2563: mah+aa b+ha ling ta la kha hi /
NK030(a)005:2565: gsum pa bzlas pa bskul tshig dang /
NK030(a)005:2568: man ngag mdo lung rgyud dang bcas pa yis //
NK030(a)005:2569: ting 'dzin bla ma rnams kyi thugs kha nas //
NK030(a)005:2570: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK030(a)005:2573: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub gsol //
NK030(a)005:2575: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram gyi li h+aum //
NK030(a)005:2576: badz+ra yo gi gu ru sa ma ya dza //
NK030(a)005:2577: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK030(a)005:2578: g+hu ya dz+ny+aa na b+ho d+he tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum /
NK030(a)005:2580: h+aum rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK030(a)005:2581: lhun grub phyag chen tshe rnam smin //
NK030(a)005:2582: rgya gar bod kyi grub thob tshogs bcas pa'i //
NK030(a)005:2583: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dngos grub 'dir stsool cig /
NK030(a)005:2585: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyis rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang ba'i lha
NK030(a)005:2586: tshogs rnams la dngos grub du gsol ba'i mdo ni
NK030(a)005:2587: / zhes pa la sogs pa rnams gong ji lta ba bzhin bya'o //
NK030(a)005:2593: gsum pas 'od du zhu nas bdag nyid la thim pas /
NK030(a)005:2594: bdag la sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las kyis gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK030(a)005:2595: de ltar cho ga'i rim pa rnams tshar ba dang /
NK030(a)005:2597: dpon slob rnam grangs mnyam par bkram la //
NK030(a)005:2598: de'i bar la slob bu rnams khrus rim zhig bya nang du sleb pa dang /
NK030(a)005:2602: rnal 'byor pa rnams rol la dbang bskur ro //
NK030(a)005:2604: de nas zhal zas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK030(a)005:2605: las mkhan gyi tshogs mchod zur tsam byas la //
NK030(a)005:2606: zla kham zhabs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)005:2607: rang rig ye shes mngon snang ba'i /
NK030(a)005:2609: / 'dod yon gsal ba'i longs spyod brgyan //
NK030(a)005:2610: yongs su rdzogs pa'i sid+d+hii bstsol //
NK030(a)005:2611: bdag nyid rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral
NK030(a)005:2612: rnams kyis rdo rje tshe gsol bas tshe dbang phun
NK030(a)005:2613: sum tshogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan par gyur cig
NK030(a)005:2614: / mah+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyis dbang phyug chen po thob par gyur cig  /
NK030(a)005:2617: / 'gro ba mang po dbang du 'du bar gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:2618: zla rgyas gsol bas tshogs gnyis rgyun du rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:2619: gal phye gsol bas bsam pa thams cad lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:2620: zla phrom gsol bas gsang ba chos nyid zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par gyur cig  /
NK030(a)005:2621: 'jam des gsol bas byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:2625: ro rnam pa sna tshogs gsol bas zhi khro sprul pa'i tshogs la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:2626: thugs rje chen pos dgongs zhing bzhes nas bdag nyid la /
NK030(a)005:2627: sku gsung thugs kyi sid d+hi dus da lta nyid du thob par bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:2628: zhes brjod la sid+d+hi'i zhal zas rnams kun gyi rim par bstsal du gsol //
NK030(a)005:2629: zhes brjod la sid d+hi'i zhal zas kun gyi rim pa gsol lo //
NK030(a)005:2630: de nas dngos grub kyi lhag ma gsum la //
NK030(a)005:2631: yid dam lha'i skal ba rdo rje slob dpon gyis rol //
NK030(a)005:2632: dal lha'i skal ba rgyas theb la byin //
NK030(a)005:2633: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi skal ba de //
NK030(a)005:2634: de na yod pa'i slob bu las can cig la sbyin no //
NK030(a)005:2635: de nas gzhan rnams ci rigs par sbyin la spyad /
NK030(a)005:2636: ka ya wa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK030(a)005:2638: sid+hi brtan par bya ba'i phyir dang //
NK030(a)005:2639: sems can gyi don bya ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)005:2640: me tog lag tu 'grim la rten 'brel snying pos rab gnas byed do //
NK030(a)005:2641: de nas mar me blangs la /
NK030(a)005:2642: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs la sogs pa rnams kyis /
NK030(a)005:2644: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang //
NK030(a)005:2645: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang //
NK030(a)005:2646: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang //
NK030(a)005:2647: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK030(a)005:2648: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes dang //
NK030(a)005:2649: klong du gyur pa'i ye shes dang //
NK030(a)005:2650: dbyings su sgrol ba'i ye shes dang //
NK030(a)005:2651: ma 'gags thugs kyi ye shes dang //
NK030(a)005:2652: thugs ye shes dgu'i nang nas 'char ba'i sid+d+hi bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK030(a)005:2654: lcam dral rnams kyis thob par mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)005:2657: de nas mar me'i smon lam gdab ba ni /
NK030(a)005:2658: kun gyi srin lag sbrel zhing mar me 'dzin la /
NK030(a)005:2659: h+aum dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK030(a)005:2660: rdo rje slob dpon gnyen gyi dbu gzung nas //
NK030(a)005:2661: rgyal ba'i gdung tshob mched dang lcam dral rnams //
NK030(a)005:2662: nam zhig byang chub lam du zhugs ba'i tshe /
NK030(a)005:2664: / 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chen po'i mi gtung zhing //
NK030(a)005:2665: gcan ga zan gdug pa'i sgra skad mi grags dang //
NK030(a)005:2666: ma rig mun pa'i nang du mi btang zhing //
NK030(a)005:2667: gcong rong zab mo'i nang du mi skye dang //
NK030(a)005:2668: dmyal ba'i zangs khar nang du mi ltung zhing //
NK030(a)005:2669: mtshon rnon gdug pa'i dbal gyis mi 'phog shog /
NK030(a)005:2670: dge ba'i bshes gnyen sku drin che ba dang //
NK030(a)005:2671: dam tshig gcig pa'i rdo rje mched lcam rnams //
NK030(a)005:2672: dam tshig dbang gis 'brel ba'i gzungs ma gsum //
NK030(a)005:2673: tshe rabs 'di dang tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK030(a)005:2674: mi 'bral 'grogs pa'i ting 'dzin rtse gcig gis //
NK030(a)005:2675: sa bcu khyad par rim gyi bsgrod gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:2676: nam zhig tshe 'phos lus barjesa dus byung tshe //
NK030(a)005:2677: ma rig gti mug mun pa'i sdug bsngal rnams /
NK030(a)005:2679: / 'khor pa'i g.yang sa chen por ltung srid na //
NK030(a)005:2680: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)005:2681: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)005:2682: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po'i shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)005:2683: zhe sdang 'bar ba las kyi sdug bsngal gyis /
NK030(a)005:2684: dmyal ba'i zangs khang lam du ltung srid na //
NK030(a)005:2685: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)005:2686: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)005:2687: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po yi shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)005:2688: nga rgyal khro gtum khengs pa'i sdug bsngal gyis //
NK030(a)005:2689: gcan gzan gdug pa'i sgra skad thos srid kyis //
NK030(a)005:2690: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)005:2691: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)005:2692: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po yi shul mtshon cig  /
NK030(a)005:2693: 'dod chags 'dzin pa las kyi sdug bsngal gyis //
NK030(a)005:2694: gcong rong zab mo'i gnas su ltung srid kyis //
NK030(a)005:2695: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)005:2696: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)005:2697: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po yi shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)005:2698: phrag dog zug rngu'i las kyi sdug bsngal gyis //
NK030(a)005:2699: mtshon rno gdug pa'i spal gyi phog srid kyis //
NK030(a)005:2700: gsal ba'i mar me thugs rje der ma chung //
NK030(a)005:2701: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'di //
NK030(a)005:2702: rig 'dzin bsgrub pa po yi shul mtshon nas //
NK030(a)005:2703: sa bcu khyad par rim gyis bsgrod pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)005:2704: nyon mongs bag chags ma lus byang nas ni /
NK030(a)005:2706: / 'gro don thogs pa med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis //
NK030(a)005:2707: sa bcu khyad par rdzogs gyur nas //
NK030(a)005:2708: byang chub sems ma rnams kyis mdun bsus cig /
NK030(a)005:2709: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi mtha' skyongs shig /
NK030(a)005:2710: khro bo khro mo rnams kyis rgyab brten cig /
NK030(a)005:2711: sa bcu'i khyad par rtse mor phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)005:2712: phyir mi zlog pa'i dngos grub de thob po //
NK030(a)005:2713: kun tu 'od kyi sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)005:2714: yi dam lha'i sngon nas shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)005:2715: bkra shis lha mo brgyad kyi mtha' rten cig /
NK030(a)005:2716: ma tshogs dbang phyug ma'i mtha' skyongs shig /
NK030(a)005:2717: stug po bkod pa'i sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)005:2718: rdo rje khro rgyal rnams kyi zhal mthong nas //
NK030(a)005:2719: rig 'dzin rnams kyis zhabs drung skyes nas kyang //
NK030(a)005:2720: bla med sku gsung thugs su 'grub par smon //
NK030(a)005:2721: shes bya'i sgrib pa phra mo spangs nas ni //
NK030(a)005:2722: yi ge gsum gyi gol sa der bskod de //
NK030(a)005:2723: de bas kun tu 'od kyi sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)005:2724: che mchog he ru ka yi mdun bsus shig /
NK030(a)005:2725: gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi'i mtha' skyongs cig /
NK030(a)005:2726: yi dam lha'i rgyab nas srog rten cig /
NK030(a)005:2727: kun bzang dbyer med sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)005:2728: kun tu bzang po yab kyi mdun bsus shig /
NK030(a)005:2729: kun tu bzang mo yum gyis mtha' skyongs cig /
NK030(a)005:2730: yi dam lha yis rgyab nas srog rten cig /
NK030(a)005:2731: rdo rje sems dpa'i rig 'dzin sar phyin tshe //
NK030(a)005:2732: rgyal ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis shul mtshon nas //
NK030(a)005:2733: mnyam pa'i ting 'dzin gyis mtha' skyongs cig /
NK030(a)005:2734: yid dam lha'i rgyab nas srog rten cig /
NK030(a)005:2735: lcang lo can gyi sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)005:2736: dbyer med ting nge 'dzin gyi shul mtshon cig /
NK030(a)005:2737: bsgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis mtha' skyongs shig /
NK030(a)005:2738: rdzogs pa bla ma'i sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)005:2739: khyab brdal rig 'dzin rnams kyi shul mtshon cig  /
NK030(a)005:2740: 'ub chub ting nge 'dzin gyi mtha' bsdus shig /
NK030(a)005:2741: srid gsum ngang rdzogs sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)005:2742: thig le chen po'i ngang du lhun grub nas //
NK030(a)005:2743: bya brtsol gnyis kyi mtha' las der 'das tshe /
NK030(a)005:2744: chos sku skye ba med pa'i don thob nas //
NK030(a)005:2745: longs sku sprul skus 'gro don byed par shog /
NK030(a)005:2746: ces smon lam rgya chen po btab bo //
NK030(a)005:2747: de nas dngos grub kyi drin lan gso ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)005:2748: tshogs la sogs pa yon phul ste /
NK030(a)005:2749: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK030(a)005:2751: rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung las kyang //
NK030(a)005:2752: che ba rgyal srid dang yul 'khor //
NK030(a)005:2753: gces pa bu smad dang phyag rgya ma /
NK030(a)005:2754: 'phangs pa nor dang dbyig dka' ba lus dang srog /
NK030(a)005:2756: rgyun du zas dang gos yun du dad pa dang dam tshig /
NK030(a)005:2757: zhu khar srid zhu dang gus pa //
NK030(a)005:2758: mchog du brtse sems dang gdung ba la sogs pa mnyes pa /
NK030(a)005:2759: sna tshogs chu bo'i gzhung bzhin 'bul lo //
NK030(a)005:2760: de nas gu ru'i zhabs slob bu'i spyi bor bzhag /
NK030(a)005:2761: de ring phan chod bu khyod kyis //
NK030(a)005:2762: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin gyis //
NK030(a)005:2763: nga yi bsgo ba ci ltar bzhin //
NK030(a)005:2764: bu khyod kyi ni bya dgos so //
NK030(a)005:2766: bla ma rdo rje rgyal po la //
NK030(a)005:2767: dad mos gus pa'i sems ldan pas /
NK030(a)005:2768: bka' yis ci ltar bsgo ba bzhin /
NK030(a)005:2769: lus ngag yid gsum gnyen gyis blangs /
NK030(a)005:2773: lhag ma btang las mkhan dang /
NK030(a)005:2774: mched lcam gyis phyir bstan ma skyongs //
NK030(a)005:2775: slob dpon dang rgyal thebs kyi nang du /
NK030(a)005:2776: dug gsum gyis sbyin bsregs bya /
NK030(a)005:2778: rgyal thebs kyi tho rgyal chen la ya hi ga tshas gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)005:2780: ye shes lha yi sgo byang la /
NK030(a)005:2782: bar chad bgegs kyi sgo byang /
NK030(a)005:2783: mchog phur dar gyi cod pan gcig bdud rtsi 'khyil par bskyed /
NK030(a)005:2784: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlabs la sgo byang de dkyil 'khor gyi 'og du bcug /
NK030(a)005:2785: phur ba de g+ha tas dril nas sgo byang la gdab /
NK030(a)005:2786: der bdud rtsi thig pa blug nas //
NK030(a)005:2787: byang chub kyi sems ma skyes kyi bar du thar pa med par bsam ste /
NK030(a)005:2788: des ni las rjes shis par bya ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK030(a)005:2789: de nas slob dpon kun 'dus las bkra shis bya /
NK030(a)005:2792: spyi don gnyis pa grol byed kyi gdams pa ni /
NK030(a)005:2793: thos bsam sgom gsum la rten nas khrid 'debs pa ste /
NK030(a)005:2794: bla ma'i zhal las shes par gyis shig /
NK030(a)005:2795: spyi don gsum pa rtsis che bas /
NK030(a)005:2798: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK030(a)005:2799: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK030(a)005:2802: yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa'i ston pa rdo rje
NK030(a)005:2803: rgyal po rdo rje rin chen dpal bzang pos gdams
NK030(a)005:2804: shing gtad / gang la gtad na /
NK030(a)005:2806: gang zag chos kyi mig can dang //
NK030(a)005:2807: mkha' 'gro chos skyong rnams la gtad //
NK030(a)005:2808: dgos phyed gang gi ched du gtad na /
NK030(a)005:2809: chos 'di mi nub par bya ba'i phyir bsdud pa po la gtad /
NK030(a)005:2810: chos 'di dar zhing rgyas pa'i phyir gang zag chos kyi spyan ldan la gtad /
NK030(a)005:2811: chos 'di bka' btsan byin rlabs che ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)005:2812: mkha' 'gro dang chos skyong rnams la gtad dgos so //
NK030(a)005:2813: tshul ji ltar du gtad na /
NK030(a)005:2814: de ni de yis thugs skyes phyir /
NK030(a)005:2815: de yi don ni des bsdus rigs ces gsungs pa ltar /
NK030(a)005:2816: rdo rje slob dpon gyis thugs las skyes pa'i //
NK030(a)005:2818: mtho brten myur rno rgya che yangs //
NK030(a)005:2819: zab yod rgyu'i gang zag gis /
NK030(a)005:2821: blo yi mtshan nyid bdun dang ldan pa'i bsdud pa po badz+ra b+ha tra la /
NK030(a)005:2824: ston pa rdo rje rgyal pos ci ltar gsungs pa'i don rnams /
NK030(a)005:2826: gzungs dang ldan pas bsdud pa po mdzad de /
NK030(a)005:2827: de yang thog mar klad don la /
NK030(a)005:2830: bshad par dam bca' ba dang gsum du bsdus /
NK030(a)005:2832: yid ches shing khungs btsun par bya ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)005:2834: sgyu 'phrul dbang gi rgyud pa rnams dang /
NK030(a)005:2835: lung a nu yo ga mdo dbang gi rgyud rim rnams dang /
NK030(a)005:2836: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga
NK030(a)005:2837: sems sde bco brgyad kyi dbang gi rgyud pa'i rim
NK030(a)005:2839: de las byung ba'i gdams ngag la /
NK030(a)005:2841: ma smin pa smin par byed pa /
NK030(a)005:2843: smin pa grol bar byed pa'i gdam ngag dang gsum /
NK030(a)005:2846: drug gis bsgrubs pa'i gzhi gzung ba dang /

NK030(a)005:2851: nub gsum pa dngos gzhi dang gsum /
NK030(a)005:2853: sa gzhi spyi'i mtshan nyid brtags pa dang /
NK030(a)005:2854: rang gi mtshan nyid brtags pa dang /

NK030(a)005:2858: sa byin gyis brlabs pa dang /

NK030(a)005:2876: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo la /

NK030(a)005:2909: 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa gnyis /
NK030(a)005:2910: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa la /
NK030(a)005:2911: dkyil 'khor che chung gi tshad dang /
NK030(a)005:2912: dkyil 'khor gyi thig gdab pa dang /
NK030(a)005:2915: dkyil 'khor la rab gnas byed pa dang /
NK030(a)005:2918: 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la //

NK030(a)005:2920: slob ma 'jug cing dbang bskur ba la gnyis /

NK030(a)005:2940: bzod par gsol ba dang bac+wa brgyad bac+wa brgyad du bsdus /
NK030(a)005:2941: dbang la yang phyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:2953: phyag rgya'i dbang dang bcu bcur bsdus /
NK030(a)005:2959: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang dang lnga lngar bsdus /
NK030(a)005:2962: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:2963: tshig dbang rin po che dang gsum gsum du bsdus /

NK030(a)005:2967: / 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa dang gnyis /
NK030(a)005:2969: dkyil 'khor che chung gi tshad dang /
NK030(a)005:2970: dkyil 'khor la thig gdab pa dang /
NK030(a)005:2975: sbyin sreg dang bdun bdun du bsdus /
NK030(a)005:2976: 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la //
NK030(a)005:2977: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang //
NK030(a)005:2978: slob ma dkyil 'khor zhugs cing dbang bskur ba dang gnyis /
NK030(a)005:2980: dpon slob gnyis ka la khrus la sogs pa don
NK030(a)005:2981: bco brgyad bco brgyad yon tan dang bcas pa la
NK030(a)005:2982: gnyis su bsdus / dbang la'ang phyi dbang /
NK030(a)005:2987: zhi ba phyag rgya'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:2991: bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:2992: rin chen sna bdun gyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:2994: brgyan chas rtags kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:2995: rdo rje ming gi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:2996: dbang phyug 'khor lo'i dbang bcur bsdus /
NK030(a)005:3001: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3003: rin chen sna bdun gyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3006: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3007: bkra shis rtags brgyad kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3008: thig le ming gi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3011: shes rab rigs pa gtan tshig gi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3012: snying rje rtags kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3014: dug ga sum sprugs pa'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3015: srid gsum sgrol ba'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3017: las rnams rdzogs pa'i dbang dang gnyis med 'khril ba'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3018: gsang ba sbyor ba'i dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3019: kun la dbang ba 'dod yon gyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3021: thams cad bsgrub pa rdzas kyi dbang dang //
NK030(a)005:3022: gnyis su med pa rdo rje ming gi dbang dang bcu gsum du bsdus /
NK030(a)005:3025: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gnyis su bsdus so //
NK030(a)005:3026: bzhi pa gsang ba man ngag gi chu bo la 'ang //
NK030(a)005:3027: rdzogs chen sems sde bco brgyad kyi dbang dang /
NK030(a)005:3028: zhar la 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dngos grub len pa'i cho ga dang /
NK030(a)005:3029: rdzas la brten nas sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin
NK030(a)005:3030: las kyi dngos grub len pa'i cho ga rjes chog
NK030(a)005:3032: gnyis pa grol byed kyi gdams pa la /
NK030(a)005:3033: rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po /
NK030(a)005:3034: sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad la sogs pa'i rgyud dang //
NK030(a)005:3036: man ngag phra mo drug bcu /
NK030(a)005:3037: bu lnga la sogs rnams pa dang /
NK030(a)005:3038: mdo' dgongs pa 'dus pa la sogs pa'i mdo snga ma bdun /
NK030(a)005:3043: smad 'grel mun pa'i go cha la sogs rgyud rgya gzhung man ngag rnams dang /
NK030(a)005:3047: kun byed ma bu dgu bskor la sogs rgyud rgya
NK030(a)005:3048: gzhung man nga ga dang bcas pa la thos bsam
NK030(a)005:3050: sgom pa rim pa gcig char gyis tshul du sgom pa /
NK030(a)005:3051: sbyod pa sbyod lam rnam bzhi lta b+hee la mi 'da' bar spyod /
NK030(a)005:3058: 'khor lo nyi shu rtsa lnga thob pa'i thabs zab mor bsdus so //
NK030(a)005:3059: gsum pa rtsis che ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)005:3060: bka' rgyas gdab pa 'di dag go /
NK030(a)005:3061: zhabs don la brtsam pa ji ltar bya ba'i phyir dang //
NK030(a)005:3062: brtsam pa'i dge ba bsngo zhing //
NK030(a)005:3064: brtsams pa mthar phyir pa'i rgyu mtshan dang gsum du bsdus so //
NK030(a)005:3065: gnyis pa gang zag gi spyan ldan la tshul ji ltar gtad na /
NK030(a)005:3066: rdo rje'i slob ma che ge mo dang che ge /
NK030(a)005:3067: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i brtsam dus su //
NK030(a)005:3068: rdo rje 'chang chen po gnyis pa kun bzang rtse ba //
NK030(a)005:3069: bsod nams rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po ba //
NK030(a)005:3070: drung ye shes dbang po'i sde //
NK030(a)005:3071: lhun sde rab 'byams pa dpal 'byor rgyal mtshan //
NK030(a)005:3072: lo ts+aa ba chen po grags pa mtha' yas //
NK030(a)005:3073: dang po rab 'byams ba don 'grub rgyal mtshan pa //
NK030(a)005:3074: ltar ba kun dga' dpal ldan rgyal mtshan //
NK030(a)005:3075: rab 'byams pa'i rin chen rgyal mtshan //
NK030(a)005:3076: bka' bcu pa kun dga' rgyal mtshan //
NK030(a)005:3077: sman gcig pa sku skye ba la sogs pa'i dge
NK030(a)005:3078: ba'i bshes gnyen chos kyi spyan can khyed rnams la
NK030(a)005:3079: / rdo rje slob dpon bdag gis dbang bskur //
NK030(a)005:3081: man ngag gnang ba brten nas khyed rnams kyis //
NK030(a)005:3082: spyir rgyud rgya gzhung man nga ga bye brag tu
NK030(a)005:3083: mdo rgyu sems gsum gyi dbang don zab mo 'di
NK030(a)005:3089: gzhan la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK030(a)005:3092: spel ba la sogs dar zhing rgyas par mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:3095: de ltar du mdzad pa zhal gyi bzhes shing da lan yang tshe dang che ge zhes dgos so //
NK030(a)005:3096: bye brag du phyag dpe yang /
NK030(a)005:3097: chos rje kun bzang rtse pa /
NK030(a)005:3098: drung ye shes dbang po'i sde /
NK030(a)005:3112: blo gros pa rnams kyis dbang dpe cha tshang cha bac+wa lnga bri bar zhal gyis bzhes so //
NK030(a)005:3113: gsum pa mkha' 'gro chos skyong la tshul ci ltar gtad na /
NK030(a)005:3114: rje btsun ma khros ma nag mo la sogs pa'i dkar mo sku yi mkha' 'gro //
NK030(a)005:3117: ser mo yon tan gyi mkha' 'gro //
NK030(a)005:3118: ljang mo 'phrin las kyi mkha' 'gro la sogs pa mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs //
NK030(a)005:3119: khyad par bdag cag la ma ltar byams pa'i mkha' 'gro //
NK030(a)005:3121: gzungs ltar gdung pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK030(a)005:3122: bran ltar myur ba'i mkha' 'gro ma 'khor dang bcas
NK030(a)005:3123: pa khyed rnams gyi zhal du pany+tsa a mri ta
NK030(a)005:3124: kha hi / b+ha ling ta kha hi /
NK030(a)005:3126: sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes shing tshims nas //
NK030(a)005:3127: bdag cag dpon slob yon mchod 'khor dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK030(a)005:3129: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dbang dpe 'di /
NK030(a)005:3131: / 'dzin skyong spel gsum byed pa'i gang zag rnams kyis
NK030(a)005:3132: bsrung skyob dang 'phrin las dam pa mdzad du gsol
NK030(a)005:3133: // gal te chos 'di la gnod pa byed pa ste /
NK030(a)005:3137: 'khu ba la sogs pa'i bstan dgra rnams kyi srog chod /
NK030(a)005:3140: thal ba'i rdul du barloga cig /
NK030(a)005:3142: chos skyong la gtad pa ni /
NK030(a)005:3143: ru ru ro ru pa tsa la a shug me //
NK030(a)005:3144: dpal ldan ma lha mo nag mo rang byung gi rgyal mo //
NK030(a)005:3145: bdud kyi yul gshin rje'i sring /
NK030(a)005:3147: / 'khor ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK030(a)005:3151: sku gsung thugs mnyes shing tshim nas chos 'di 'dzin
NK030(a)005:3152: skyongs spel gsum byed pa'i gang zag rnams kyi bsrungs
NK030(a)005:3153: ma dang sdong grogs rgya chen po mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:3154: chos 'di bka' btsan byin che dar zhing rgyas par mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)005:3155: chos 'di'i bstan dgra thams cad bsgral ba'i 'phrin las rgya chen po mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:3157: bur gur mah+aa pad+ma rdo bur //
NK030(a)005:3160: e ho shwa mo kro ta h+aum h+aum h+aum phata phata phata //
NK030(a)005:3161: dpal ldan mgon po nag po //
NK030(a)005:3164: lha dmag bye ba dung phyur gyi tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK030(a)005:3165: pany+tsa a mri ta kha hi /
NK030(a)005:3168: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las kyi rgyud mnyes nas //
NK030(a)005:3169: sngon dpal chen po'i spyan sngar chos 'di'i rgyud pa
NK030(a)005:3170: 'dzin pa rnams kyi bsrungs ma dang 'phrin las mdzad
NK030(a)005:3171: par khas blangs pa bzhin du bsrung ba dang 'phrin
NK030(a)005:3172: las mdzod gcig / ces gnyer gtad do //
NK030(a)005:3174: rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi zhal du /
NK030(a)005:3175: pan tsa a mri ta kha hi //
NK030(a)005:3178: khyed rnam kyis chos 'di 'dzin skyong spel ba la sogs byed pa'i gang zag rnams kyis /
NK030(a)005:3179: bsrung ma dang mthun pa'i sgo nas 'byor ba phun
NK030(a)005:3180: sum tshogs pa la longs spyod pa'i skal ba ldan
NK030(a)005:3181: par gyur cig / ces gnyer gtad do //
NK030(a)005:3182: badz+ra sa d+hu sa ma y+aa /
NK030(a)005:3183: pan tsa a mri ta la kha hi /
NK030(a)005:3188: bu dam can 'gar ba nag po sha med gangs dkar ma /
NK030(a)005:3192: yang 'khor bka'i lha ma srin sde brgyad kyi tshogs dang bcas pa khyed rnams kyis //
NK030(a)005:3193: chos 'di 'dzin skyong spel gsum byed pa'i gang zag rnams kyis bsrungs skyobs rgya chen po mdzod cig /
NK030(a)005:3194: bstan dgra sdig can rnams thal ba rdul bzhin brlag pa'i 'phrin las mdzod gcig /
NK030(a)005:3195: ces tshul de ltar du gtad do //
NK030(a)005:3197: ci ltar brtsam pa'i tshul dang /
NK030(a)005:3198: brtsams pa'i dge rtsa byang chub tu bsngo zhing //
NK030(a)005:3200: brtsams pa mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan no //
NK030(a)005:3201: dang po ci ltar brtsam pa'i tshul ni /
NK030(a)005:3203: chos kyi rgyal po spyan snga rin chen dpal //
NK030(a)005:3204: ngag dbang grags pa phyogs las rnams par rgyal //
NK030(a)005:3205: mthun rkyen bzang legs rgya che phun sum tshogs //
NK030(a)005:3206: thugs dgongs rnam dag dgyes tshul du mar bcas //
NK030(a)005:3207: thugs rje bka' drin mnyams med byin rlabs dang //
NK030(a)005:3208: thams cad mkhyen pa chos rje gzhon nu dpal //
NK030(a)005:3209: mnyes pa'i sgo nas gnang sbyin rim par bcas //
NK030(a)005:3210: bstan la phan phyir mdo rgyud sems gsum gyi //
NK030(a)005:3211: dbang mchog legs par brtsam dgos bka' brtsal dang //
NK030(a)005:3212: sprul pa'i sku mchog zha dmar cod pan 'dzin //
NK030(a)005:3213: chos kyi grags pa ye shes dpal bzang pos //
NK030(a)005:3214: dgyes pa'i tshul drug gser gyi me tog sogs //
NK030(a)005:3215: gnang nas mdo dbang bri dgos gsung ba dang //
NK030(a)005:3216: gzhung lugs rab 'byams thugs su chud pa yis //
NK030(a)005:3217: bsod nams rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po pa la sogs bshes gnyen mang pos bskul ba dang //
NK030(a)005:3218: bdag kyang lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam dag gis //
NK030(a)005:3219: bla ma rnams kyi thugs dgongs rdzogs pa dang //
NK030(a)005:3220: mkha' mnyam 'gro rnams bde skyid 'byung ba dang //
NK030(a)005:3221: myur du sangs rgyas thob par bya phyir ste //
NK030(a)005:3222: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba phun tshogs la //
NK030(a)005:3223: brten nas gsang sngags mdo rgyu sems gsum gyi //
NK030(a)005:3224: dbang gi chog 'grig bsgrubs thabs gsal bar brtsams //
NK030(a)005:3225: de 'ang ci lta bu zhe na //
NK030(a)005:3226: ka thog chos kyi rgya mtsho chu yi gter //
NK030(a)005:3227: thos bsam sgom gsum srubs las legs par 'khrungs //
NK030(a)005:3228: sngags 'chang rdo rje 'dzin pa tsha zer rgyas //
NK030(a)005:3229: rta bdun mkha' la dbus kyi ri rgyal skor //
NK030(a)005:3230: gdul bya mdo rgyud pad tshal rgyas par byas //
NK030(a)005:3231: rnams dpyod blo yis bung ba rdo rje mchus //
NK030(a)005:3232: rgyud gzhung man ngag bcud rnams du ma bsdus //
NK030(a)005:3233: dbang mchog sbrang rtsi'i rgya mtsho yon tan tshangs //
NK030(a)005:3234: e ma 'di la mi sems su zhig yod //
NK030(a)005:3235: e ma 'di yi ro mchog myong bar byos //
NK030(a)005:3236: gnyis pa brtsams pa'i dge rtsa byang chub du bsngo zhing smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK030(a)005:3237: de ltar brtsam pa'i dge rtsa dri med dang /
NK030(a)005:3239: / 'khor 'das lam gsum bsdus pa'i dge rtsa gnyis //
NK030(a)005:3240: phyogs gcig sdom pa kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin //
NK030(a)005:3241: zhi bar gshegs pa rtsa ba'i bla ma dang //
NK030(a)005:3242: brgyud pa'i bla ma thugs rje can rnams la //
NK030(a)005:3243: lus ngag yid gsum mos pas phul ba yis //
NK030(a)005:3244: sa las yon tan gong du 'phel ba dang //
NK030(a)005:3245: rdo rje 'chang bar myur du gshegs nas kyang //
NK030(a)005:3246: bdag sogs 'gro rnams 'dren ston mdzad gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3247: yangs gcig brtsams pa'i dge rtsa dri med dang //
NK030(a)005:3248: sbyin pa tshul khrims sgom las byung ba yis /
NK030(a)005:3249: rab dkar dge ba'i tshogs rnams bsam las 'das //
NK030(a)005:3250: gzhan yang phyogs bcu'i dge tshogs phyogs gcig sdom //
NK030(a)005:3251: kun tu bzang po mchod pa'i sprin phung gis //
NK030(a)005:3252: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po mnyes phyir 'bul //
NK030(a)005:3253: de las byung ba'i mthu stobs byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)005:3254: sku la mtshan mchog bzang po sum cu gnyis //
NK030(a)005:3255: dpe byad bzang po brgyad bcus rab tu spras //
NK030(a)005:3256: dag pa'i 'khor tshogs nam mkha'i skar tshogs bkra /
NK030(a)005:3257: sku mchog rgyan gyis 'khor lo thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3258: gsung la dbyangs kyi yan lag drug cu dang //
NK030(a)005:3259: chos kyi dung chen gsung lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK030(a)005:3260: chos kyi grags pas phyogs bcur khyab gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3261: gsung mchog brgyan gyi 'khor lo thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3262: thugs ni ci lta ci rnyed dbyer med mkhyen //
NK030(a)005:3263: chos dbyings me long mnyam nyid so sor rtogs //
NK030(a)005:3264: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK030(a)005:3265: ting 'dzin 'bum phrag du ma thugs chud pa'i //
NK030(a)005:3266: thugs mchog brgyan gyi 'khor lo thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3267: sna tshogs rin chen sa gzhi mnan na nem //
NK030(a)005:3268: bteg na 'phar la mig mang ris su bris //
NK030(a)005:3269: rgya mdo thams cad rin chen tshom bus spras //
NK030(a)005:3270: ltar mi bzod pa'i 'od dang ldan pa yis //
NK030(a)005:3271: yon tan zhing khams sna tshogs thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3272: rat+na sna tshogs las grub gzhal yas khang //
NK030(a)005:3273: gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs chos 'khor gdugs //
NK030(a)005:3274: brgyan rnams sna tshogs du mas spras pa yi //
NK030(a)005:3275: gzhal yas yon tan ldan pa thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3276: rin po che'i khri la mdzod mig ldan //
NK030(a)005:3277: seng ge glang chen rta mchog rma bya dang //
NK030(a)005:3278: shang shang brgyad brgyad rnams kyi btegs pa'i steng //
NK030(a)005:3279: mu thig dra ba la sogs khri khebs ldan //
NK030(a)005:3280: pad+ma stong ldan nyi ma zla ba yis //
NK030(a)005:3281: gdan khri yon tan can la bzhugs gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3282: dar dang rin chen rus pa du ma yis //
NK030(a)005:3283: dbu rgyan snyan cha mgur chu phreng ba dang //
NK030(a)005:3284: dpung rgyan phyag gdub zhabs gdub sor gdub sogs //
NK030(a)005:3285: rgyan cha yon tan ldan pas rgyan gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3286: sngon po dkar po ser po dmar po ljang //
NK030(a)005:3287: nyi shu rtsa lnga stong phrag du ma yis //
NK030(a)005:3288: mdzes shing yid du 'ong ba gur du phub /
NK030(a)005:3290: / 'od zer yon tan ldan pa 'phro gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3291: nad dang gdon dang sdig sgrib thams cad dang //
NK030(a)005:3292: dgra dang bgegs dang bar du gcod pa yis //
NK030(a)005:3293: spangs bar 'os pa ci mchis thams cad kun //
NK030(a)005:3294: zhi pa'i 'phrin las chen po 'grub gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3295: tshe dang bsod nams bkrag dang gzi brjid dang /
NK030(a)005:3297: / 'khor dang longs spyod dpal dang 'byor pa dang //
NK030(a)005:3298: nyams dang rtogs pa sku dang ye shes sogs //
NK030(a)005:3299: rgyas pa'i 'phrin las thams cad 'grub gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3300: lha 'dre mi gsum khams gsum srid pa gsum //
NK030(a)005:3301: zas nor longs spyod 'dod dgu gang dgos pa //
NK030(a)005:3302: ji ltar 'os ba'i dngos po thams cad kun //
NK030(a)005:3303: dbang du 'dus pa'i 'phrin las thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3304: nang gi nad gdon sdig sgrib bag chags dang //
NK030(a)005:3305: phyi nas sdo ba'i dgra bo dmag tshogs dang //
NK030(a)005:3306: bgegs kyi rigs la stong phrag brgyad bcu dang //
NK030(a)005:3307: ye 'brogs sum brgya dang ni drug bcu sogs //
NK030(a)005:3308: drag pos thams cad brdul du brlag gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3309: yang gcig dge rtsa mchod sprin rgya mtsho yis //
NK030(a)005:3310: rtsa ba'i bla ma bka' drin chen po dang //
NK030(a)005:3311: gnas lnga pan chen mngon dga' chos rdzong pa //
NK030(a)005:3312: zhwa dmar cod pan 'dzin pa bzhi pa ba //
NK030(a)005:3313: bshes gnyen rgya mtsho dang bcas rnams la 'bul //
NK030(a)005:3314: spangs rtogs mthar phyin rdo rje 'chang thob nas /
NK030(a)005:3316: / 'gro drug sems can thar lam bkod gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3317: yang gcig 'di ltar bsgrub pa'i dge rtsa des //
NK030(a)005:3318: dkyil 'khor gcig tu zhugs pa skal bar ldan //
NK030(a)005:3319: thams cad kun rig kun bzang rtse pa sogs //
NK030(a)005:3320: rig 'dzin bsgrub mchog 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK030(a)005:3321: mtho ris yon tan bdun ldan thob nas kyang //
NK030(a)005:3322: sku lnga lhun grub tshe gcig mngon sangs rgyas /
NK030(a)005:3324: / 'khor ba ma stongs bar du brten mdzad pa'i //
NK030(a)005:3325: ded dpon dam pa mchog ni thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3326: de rnams las byung dge ba'i rtsa ba des //
NK030(a)005:3327: dus gsum pha ma sbyin bdag grogs mched dang //
NK030(a)005:3328: zab don chos dang dkar nag las kyis 'brel //
NK030(a)005:3329: sgrib gsum bag chags bcas pa dag nas kyang //
NK030(a)005:3330: nye 'khor dam pa nyid du sangs ni rgyas gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3331: gzhan yang 'gro drug sems can thams cad rnams //
NK030(a)005:3332: myur du sangs rgyas go 'phang thob gyur cig /
NK030(a)005:3335: byang chub sems dpa' tog dkar gyis //
NK030(a)005:3336: rgyal tshab mi pham mgon po la //
NK030(a)005:3337: dbu la srog zhu phul ba ltar //
NK030(a)005:3338: chos kyi rgyal po blon 'khor bcas //
NK030(a)005:3339: bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen sogs //

NK030(a)005:3864: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)005:3866: / 'khor la po tis dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)005:3867: chos kyi sgo la mkhas pa ltar /
NK030(a)005:3870: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs kyis /
NK030(a)005:3872: / 'khor la rdor dril dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)005:3873: ye shes chos dbyings rtogs par ltar /
NK030(a)005:3876: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs kyis /
NK030(a)005:3878: / 'khor la brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)005:3879: chos kyi rgyal srid thob pa ltar /
NK030(a)005:3882: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)005:3884: / 'khor la dbu brgyan dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)005:3885: mi 'jigs pa la mnga' mnyes ltar /
NK030(a)005:3888: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs gis /
NK030(a)005:3890: / 'khor la zhabs gdub dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)005:3891: stobs bcu mnga' mnyes dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)005:3894: ri rab rtse mor rnam snang gis /
NK030(a)005:3896: / 'khor la phyag gdub dbang bskur pas //
NK030(a)005:3897: tshul khrims rnam dag dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)005:3900: ri rab rtse mor kun rigs kyis /
NK030(a)005:3902: / 'khor la do shal dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)005:3903: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa ltar /
NK030(a)005:3906: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)005:3908: / 'khor la cod pan dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)005:3909: brdul gyi bag chags bral ba ltar /
NK030(a)005:3912: ri rab rtse mor snang mdzad kyis /
NK030(a)005:3914: / 'khor la ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)005:3915: rdo rje 'chang gi dbang thob ltar /
NK030(a)005:3918: ri rab rtse mor don 'grub la //
NK030(a)005:3919: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)005:3920: rnam snang nyid du sangs rgyas ltar /
NK030(a)005:3923: sku lnga lhun grub rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang /
NK030(a)005:3924: gsung lnga lhun grub dam chos rgya mtsho dang //
NK030(a)005:3925: thugs lnga lhun grub rgyal sras smin pa'i tshogs /
NK030(a)005:3927: / 'dir 'tshogs dpon slob rnams kyis bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)005:3928: rdzogs sangs rgyas nas da lta'i bar //
NK030(a)005:3929: bum chu gcig nas gcig byo dang //
NK030(a)005:3930: mar me gcig nas gcig spar bzhin //
NK030(a)005:3931: dus rgyun 'chad med pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)005:3932: gsum pa brtsam pa mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK030(a)005:3933: kun bzang rdo rje 'chang chen nas //
NK030(a)005:3934: bdag gi bar du rim pa bzhin //
NK030(a)005:3935: snyan brgyud gdams pa ma 'chugs pa'i //
NK030(a)005:3936: cho ga rim bzhin bri tshar bas //
NK030(a)005:3937: dam bca' dang po sangs pa yis //
NK030(a)005:3938: dbang gi chu bo rnam pa bzhi //
NK030(a)005:3939: rgya mtsho chen por bskyil ba yis //
NK030(a)005:3940: legs bshad rim pa tshar ba dang //
NK030(a)005:3941: dam bca' gnyis pa sangs pa yin //
NK030(a)005:3942: phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa lnga //
NK030(a)005:3943: bsnyen pa dang ni nye ba'i bsnyen //
NK030(a)005:3944: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NK030(a)005:3945: legs par bkod pa gsum pa sangs //
NK030(a)005:3946: re shig bshad du ma mchis pas //
NK030(a)005:3947: rdzogs so zhes ni tha snyad brjod //
NK030(a)005:3948: bkra shis dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK030(a)005:3949: phan thogs 'dzam gling brgyan gyur cig /
